ling%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20between%202022%20and%202023%2C%20fresh%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fec-releases-data-on-parties-redeeming-ebs-in-first-year-plea-in-sc-says-release-buyers-names-too%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20uploaded%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20have%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdhering%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-registry-gives-sealed-cover-electoral-bonds-data-back-to-election-commission-5251258%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESupreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20directive%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20commission%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017)%20uploaded%20on%20its%20website%20the%20submissions%20made%20by%20the%20political%20parties%20in%202023%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20that%20they%20had%20received%20through%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI).%20Those%20submissions%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20the%20top%20court%20by%20the%20commission%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthedailyguardian.com%2Fec-to-submit-electoral-bonds-details-to-sc-in-sealed-cover%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20sealed%20covers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20November%202023%20to%20maintain%20the%20confidentiality%20clause%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%20brought%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20details%20furnished%20by%20the%20parties%20were%20from%20April%202019%20to%20November%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20DMK%20treasurer%20and%20party%20MP%20T.R.%20Baalu%E2%80%99s%20submission%20to%20the%20ECI%20on%20November%2011%2C%202023%2C%20the%20SBI%2C%20which%20had%20issued%20bonds%20to%20the%20buyers%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%9Crequire%20the%20details%20of%20the%20donor%20to%20be%20furnished%20to%20the%20donee%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20circumstances%2C%20the%20donors%20did%20not%20strictly%20adhere%20to%20the%20requirement%20of%20furnishing%20their%20details%20whenever%20they%20handed%20over%20the%20electoral%20bond%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Baluu%20had%20stated%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20adding%2C%20that%20the%20party%20was%2C%20however%2C%20able%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccollect%20the%20details%20from%20them%E2%80%9D%20on%20time%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20call.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20details%20in%20the%20submission%20showed%20that%20Santiago%20Martin%E2%80%99s%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%20had%20donated%20Rs%2060%20crores%20to%20the%20DMK%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20between%20October%2023-29%2C%202020%20and%20a%20staggering%20Rs%20249%20crore%20between%20April%205%2C%202021%20and%20January%201%2C%202022.%20The%20DMK%20government%2C%20with%20M.K.%20Stalin%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20was%20formed%20after%20the%20April%202021%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202021-2022%20financial%20year%2C%20the%20Coimbatore-based%20company%20had%20picked%20electoral%20bonds%20to%20fund%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20for%20Rs%20309%20crores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20company%20pumped%20in%20more%20funds%20with%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%20185%20crores%20donated%20to%20the%20party%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20company%20once%20again%20donated%20Rs%2040%20crores%20to%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20submissions%2C%20between%202020%20and%202023%2C%20it%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20534%20crores%20to%20the%20DMK%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerusing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Felection-commission-uploads-electoral-bonds-data-on-website-as-per-supreme-courts-direction-252331%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20SBI%E2%80%99s%20data%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20till%20January%202024%2C%20the%20Future%20Gaming%20group%2C%20having%20spent%20a%20cumulative%20sum%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fsantiago-martin-aka-lottery-king-the-business-tycoon-who-topped-the-list-of-electoral-bond-donors%2Farticle67953870.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%201%2C368%20crores%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20came%20across%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20donor%20to%20political%20parties%20through%20the%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20another%20company%2C%20Mega%20Infrastructure%20Developers%20Private%20Limited%2C%20registered%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Panchsheel%20Enclave%2C%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20105%20crores%20between%20April%202019%20and%202022%20to%20the%20DMK.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20company%2C%20identified%20as%20only%20Triveni%2C%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20DMK%E2%80%99s%20coffers%20Rs%208%20crores%20between%202019%20and%202022.%20A%20clasp%20of%20other%20companies%2C%20seemingly%20dealing%20with%20cement%20manufacturing%2C%20also%20donated%20a%20cumulative%20sum%20of%20Rs%2019%20crores%20to%20DMK%20through%20bonds.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Sun%20TV%20Network%20of%20Kalanidhi%20Maran%20also%20featured%20in%20the%20list%20of%20donors%2C%20having%20made%20a%20one-time%20payment%20of%20Rs%2010%20crores%20in%202021-22.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20total%20amount%20the%20party%20stated%20to%20have%20received%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20between%20April%202019%20and%20November%202023%20stood%20at%20Rs.%20706%20crores.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAIDMK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20freshly%20released%20data%2C%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20Cricket%20Limited%20donated%20Rs%205%20crores%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIDMK)%20party%20in%202019.%20The%20bonds%20purchased%20by%20India%20Cement%20Limited-owned%20CSK%20on%20April%203%2C%202019%20were%20encashed%20on%20the%2012th%20of%20the%20same%20month.%20Two%20bonds%20purchased%20were%20of%20denomination%20R.%201%20crore%20each%20and%20the%20rest%20were%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakhs%20each.%20The%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20India%20Cement%20donated%20as%20additional%20Rs%2010%20crores%20to%20the%20ruling%20MK%20Stalin-led%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENarayanaswami%20Srinivasan%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20ICL%20has%20also%20been%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20and%20former%20President%20of%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI).%20In%20September%20last%20year%2C%20Srinivasan%20and%20his%20family%20became%20the%20promoters%20of%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20Cricket%20Ltd.%20(CSK)%2C%20the%20designated%20owner%20of%20the%20Chennai%20team%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%20India%20Cements%E2%80%99%20annual%20report%20shows%20that%20Srinivasan%20and%20his%20family%20own%2028.14%25%20of%20CSK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20carried%20out%20raids%20at%20the%20office%20of%20India%20Cements%20Capital%20Limited%2C%20an%20associate%20company%20of%20ICL%2C%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20however%2C%20had%20termed%20the%20search%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnormal%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Findia-cements-says-ed-searches-related-to-normal-course-transactions%2Farticle67804436.ece%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20soon%20after%20the%20raid%2C%20ICL%20claimed%3A%20%E2%80%9CICCL%20is%20an%20authorised%20dealer%20in%20providing%20forex%20services%20and%20has%20been%20providing%20these%20services%20to%20its%20clients%20complying%20with%20rules%20framed%20by%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%20ICCL%2C%20being%20one%20of%20the%20associates%20of%20The%20India%20Cements%20Limited%2C%20ED%20officials%20raised%20certain%20queries%20with%20us%20and%20we%20have%20provided%20necessary%20clarifications%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710679427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdmk-got-at-least-rs-504-crore-from-future-gaming-group-in-electoral-bonds-ec-data-reveals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20company%2C%20Mega%20Infrastructure%20Developers%20Private%20Limited%2C%20donated%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%20105%20crores%20between%20April%202019%20and%202022%20to%20the%20DMK.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Czechs%20struggle%20to%20contain%20surge%20of%20whooping%20cough%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710679386000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE8CA%2Fproduction%2F_132949595_gettyimages-1140145923.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prague's%20elderly%20mayor%20coughs%20and%20splutters%20during%20a%20public%20meeting%20as%20authorities%20battle%20increase.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68591537.amp%22%7