llies%20for%20forgetting%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attacks%20and%20vowed%20to%20continue%20Gaza%20offensive%20taking%20it%20to%20Rafah..%20He%20reaffirmed%20commitment%20to%20Rafah%20operations%20and%20said%20that%20the%20military%20operation%20would%20continue%20along%20with%20hostages%20rescue%2C%20and%20reducing%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Asks%20Ministers%20To%20Work%20On%20Roadmap%20For%20New%20Government%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20projecting%20confidence%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20has%20asked%20his%20ministers%20to%20draft%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20first%20100%20days%20and%20next%20five%20years%20for%20a%20new%20government.%20The%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20for%20a%20third%20straight%20term%20in%20power%20in%20the%20elections%20that%20were%20announced%20yesterday%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20The%20polls%20will%20begin%20on%20April%2019%20and%20end%20on%20June%201.%20The%20results%20are%20due%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20at%20a%20cabinet%20meeting%20this%20morning%2C%20PM%20Modi%20asked%20the%20ministers%20to%20meet%20secretaries%20and%20other%20officials%20of%20their%20department%20to%20discuss%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20has%20already%20announced%20multiple%20goals%20for%20a%20third%20term%20--%20including%C2%A0%20making%20India%20the%20world's%20third%20largest%20economy%20by%20boosting%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%2C%20increasing%20control%20over%20supply%20chains%2C%20and%20creating%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20replying%20to%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20motion%20of%20thanks%20on%20the%20President's%20address%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20budget%20session%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20in%20the%20third%20term%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20India%20will%20become%20the%20world's%20third-largest%20economy%2C%20up%20from%20its%20current%20fifth%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20also%20initiated%20the%20process%20of%20notifying%20the%20dates%20of%20the%20seven-phase%20parliamentary%20elections%20today%20by%20sending%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20recommendation%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20first%20notification%20will%20be%20issued%20on%20March%2020%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polls%20on%20April%2019%20on%20102%20seats.%20The%20nomination%20process%20begins%20for%20a%20particular%20phase%20with%20the%20issuance%20of%20the%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710679140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fhhbaa23_pm-modi-pti_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-asks-ministers-to-meet-officials-to-implement-roadmap-for-1st-100-days-sources-5256363%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20projecting%20confidence%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20has%20asked%20his%20ministers%20to%20draft%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20first%20100%20days%20and%20next%20five%20years%20for%20a%20new%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-asks-ministers-to-meet-officials-to-implement-roadmap-for-1st-100-days-sources-5256363%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-asks-ministers-to-meet-officials-to-implement-roadmap-for-1st-100-days-sources-5256363%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-asks-ministers-to-meet-officials-to-implement-roadmap-for-1st-100-days-sources-5256363%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Views%20on%20Political%20Funding%20Foreshadowed%20Crony%20Capitalism%20in%20New%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FModi-Adani-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20enormous%20amount%20of%20money%20was%20amassed%20from%20companies%20through%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20they%20were%20profitable%20or%20incurring%20losses%2C%20facilitated%20by%20the%20removal%20of%20the%207.5%25%20limit%20on%20the%20average%20of%20three%20years%E2%80%99%20profit%20that%20could%20be%20used%20for%20funding%20political%20parties.%20Notably%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20alone%20has%20accumulated%20approximately%20Rs%206%2C600%20crores%2C%20significantly%20more%20than%20what%20other%20national%20and%20regional%20parties%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20and%20other%20details%20of%20such%20funding%20was%20kept%20hidden%20from%20the%20public%20%E2%80%93%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20voters%E2%80%99%20fundamental%20right%20to%20information%20as%20well%20as%20the%20right%20to%20make%20an%20informed%20choice%20before%20casting%20their%20votes.%20Curiously%2C%20only%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20had%20access%20to%20the%20sources%20and%20details%20regarding%20the%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20its%20landmark%20judgement%2C%20declared%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20as%20unconstitutional%20and%20held%20that%20it%20created%20conditions%20for%20%E2%80%9Cpermitting%20the%20unregulated%20influence%20of%20companies%20in%20the%20governance%20and%20political%20process%20violating%20the%20principle%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%E2%80%9D%20Such%20categorical%20indictment%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%20is%20a%20first%20of%20its%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20political%20funding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20regime%20made%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%20completely%20opaque%20by%20the%20instrumentality%20of%20law%2C%20impairing%20a%20fair%20and%20free%20election%20process.%20To%20assess%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20vitiated%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20one%20must%20place%20this%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20Congress%20getting%20funds%20from%20business%20houses%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20early%20as%201931%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20worried%20that%20political%20parties%20might%20expend%20a%20disproportionately%20high%20amount%20of%20money%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9Cmanaging%20elections%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20illuminating%20to%20recall%20that%20on%20September%2017%2C%201931%2C%20while%20attending%20the%20second%20round%20table%20conference%20in%20London%2C%20he%20expressed%20grave%20concern%20that%20political%20parties%20would%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20using%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20only%20on%20managing%20elections%20and%20very%20critically%20remarked%20that%20that%20a%20candidate%20spending%20Rs%2060%2C000-1%20lakh%20for%20contesting%20elections%20in%20a%20poor%20country%20like%20India%20would%20be%20nothing%20but%20atrocious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20Gandhi%20been%20alive%2C%20and%20seen%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20was%20made%20in%20to%20law%20by%20committing%20multiple%20unconstitutional%20measures%20%E2%80%93%20involving%20amendments%20to%20Companies%20Act%20of%202013%2C%20Representation%20of%20People%20Act%2C%20RBI%20Act%20and%20Income%20Tax%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20he%20would%20have%20been%20aghast%20that%20what%20he%20apprehended%20in%201931%20had%20come%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20expressing%20his%20anxieties%20about%20the%20staggering%20expenditure%20on%20elections%2C%20Gandhi%20had%20no%20hesitation%20in%20conceding%20that%20Congress%20was%20being%20funded%20by%20business%20houses.%20It%20is%20instructive%20to%20peep%20into%20his%20interview%20with%20American%20journalist%20Louis%20Fischer%2C%20who%2C%20in%201942%2C%20wanted%20a%20clarification%20from%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20accusations%20that%20Congress%20was%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20big%20business%20houses%20and%20that%20he%20himself%20was%20being%20given%20money%20by%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20mill%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20been%20acclaimed%20for%20his%20adherence%20to%20truth%2C%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20they%20are%20true.%E2%80%9D%20He%20explained%20that%20Congress%2C%20which%20relied%20on%20contributions%20of%20four%20%3Cem%3Eannas%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20year%2C%20found%20the%20amounts%20collected%20from%20its%20member%20quite%20inadequate%20for%20implementing%20its%20manifold%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFischer%20then%20asked%20a%20very%20sensitive%20question%20to%20ascertain%20if%20the%20funds%20being%20given%20by%20business%20houses%20had%20contributed%20to%20alter%20and%20shape%20Congress%E2%80%99%20politics.%20Gandhi%20was%20frank%20enough%20to%20acknowledge%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20a%20silent%20debt%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20forcefully%20and%20unequivocally%20told%20Fischer%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20actually%2C%20we%20are%20very%20little%20influenced%20by%20the%20thinking%20of%20the%20rich.%20They%20are%20sometimes%20afraid%20of%20our%20demand%20for%20full%20independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20statement%2C%20that%20there%20was%20no%20quid%20pro%20quo%20involved%20between%20Congress%20and%20big%20business%20houses%2C%20stands%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20massive%20alignment%20of%20Modi%20regime%20with%20companies%20funding%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds.%20While%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20statement%20in%201942%20flagged%20the%20autonomy%20of%20Congress%E2%80%99%20politics%20from%20money%2C%20his%20comment%20on%20big%20businesses%20fearing%20complete%20independence%20revealed%C2%A0%20their%20connection%20and%20collusion%20with%20the%20British%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20historical%20insight%20form%20Fischer%E2%80%99s%20interview%20of%20Gandhi%20is%20very%20refreshing.%20It%20is%20remarkable%20to%20fathom%20the%20havoc%20caused%20by%20the%20unconstitutional%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%2C%20scripted%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20to%20critically%20evaluate%20crony%20capitalism%20sustained%20in%20a%20calculated%20manner%20as%20well%20as%20the%20quid%20pro%20quo%20between%20companies%20funding%20political%20parties%20and%20politics%20of%20BJP%20and%20other%20regimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K%20R%20Narayanan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710678615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FModi-Adani-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgandhis-views-on-political-funding-foreshadowed-crony-capitalism-in-new-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20early%20as%201931%2C%20Gandhi%20was%20worried%20that%20political%20parties%20might%20expend%20a%20disproportionately%20high%20amount%20of%20money%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%E2%80%9Cmanaging%20elections%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgandhis-views-on-political-funding-foreshadowed-crony-capitalism-in-new-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Received%20Rs%206%2C986%20Crore%20Through%20Poll%20Bonds%2C%20Highest%20Among%20All%20Parties%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20received%20the%20maximum%20funds%20through%20these%20bonds%20at%20Rs%206%2C986.5%20crore%20since%20they%20were%20introduced%20in%202018%2C%20followed%20by%20West%20Bengal's%20ruling%20party%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(Rs%201%2C397%20crore)%2C%20Congress%20(Rs%201%2C334%20crore)%20and%20BRS%20(Rs%201%2C322%20crore).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20purchaser%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20Future%20Gaming%20and%20Hotel%20Services%2C%20don