d%2Feurope%2Frussia-boosts-navy-firepower-to-counter-ukrainian-drone-attacks%2Famp_articleshow%2F108562974.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-boosts-navy-firepower-to-counter-ukrainian-drone-attacks%2Famp_articleshow%2F108562974.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FIR%20Against%20Chhattisgarh%20Ex%20Chief%20Minister%20In%20Mahadev%20Betting%20App%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20(EOW)%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20has%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20and%20others%20in%20the%20alleged%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20scam%20based%20on%20a%20probe%20report%20submitted%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%2C%20which%20has%20been%20investigating%20the%20Mahadev%20app-linked%20money%20laundering%20case%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20alleged%20in%20the%20past%20that%20its%20probe%20has%20shown%20involvement%20of%20various%20high-ranking%20politicians%20and%20bureaucrats%20from%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20the%20two%20main%20promoters%20of%20the%20app%20hail%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20projected%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20in%20this%20case%20are%20about%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ED%20has%20been%20investigating%20the%20case%20and%20based%20on%20its%20report%20submitted%20to%20the%20state's%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%2FAnti-Corruption%20Bureau%2C%20the%20FIR%20was%20registered%20against%20Baghel%20and%20others%20at%20the%20EOW%20police%20station%20here%20on%20March%204%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20EOW%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaghel%2C%20the%20senior%20Congress%20leader%2C%20along%20with%20the%20app%20promoters%20Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20Saurabh%20Chandrakar%2C%20Shubham%20Soni%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%20Agrawal%20and%2014%20others%20have%20been%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20bureaucrats%2C%20police%20officials%2C%20officers%20on%20special%20duty%20(OSDs)%20and%20other%20unidentified%20private%20persons%20have%20also%20been%20made%20accused%20(without%20being%20named)%20in%20the%20case%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20various%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20Sections%2C%20including%20120B%20(criminal%20conspiracy)%2C%20420%20(cheating)%20and%20471%20(using%20as%20genuine%20a%20forged%20document)%2C%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202018%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%2C%20citing%20the%20ED's%20report%2C%20stated%20that%20Mahadev%20Book%20App%20promoters%20Uppal%2C%20Chandrakar%2C%20Soni%20and%20Agrawal%20created%20the%20platform%20for%20live%20online%20betting%20and%20indulged%20in%20betting%20through%20Whatsapp%2C%20Facebook%20and%20Telegram%20and%20other%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promoters%20created%20different%20platforms%20and%20conducted%20illegal%20acts%20of%20online%20betting%20through%20panel%20operators%2F%20branch%20operators.%20They%20kept%2070%20to%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20illegal%20earnings%20with%20them%20and%20distributed%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20money%20to%20panel%20operators%2F%20branch%20operators%2C%20it%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20promoters%20and%20panel%20operators%20fetched%20around%20Rs%20450%20crore%20per%20month%20through%20the%20online%20betting%20app%20after%20the%20lockdown%20was%20imposed%20in%202020%20(following%20the%20outbreak%20of%20COVID-19%20pandemic)%2C%20the%20FIR%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20transaction%20of%20the%20illegally%20obtained%20money%2C%20bank%20accounts%20were%20opened%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20fake%20documents%20by%20the%20promoters%20and%20panel%20operators%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20Book%20App%20and%20hundreds%20of%20bank%20accounts%20were%20operated%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20commission%20with%20the%20money%20obtained%20from%20betting.%20The%20panel%20operators%20transferred%20illegal%20money%20to%20the%20promoters%20in%20the%20UAE%20through%20various%20bank%20accounts%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20amount%20of%20money%20was%20spent%20by%20the%20app%20promoters%20for%20advertising%20betting%20websites.%20For%20this%2C%20annual%20star-studded%20events%20were%20also%20organised%2C%20in%20which%20celebrities%20were%20involved%20by%20paying%20them%20illegal%20money%20obtained%20from%20betting%2C%20the%20FIR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20illegal%20money%20obtained%20from%20online%20betting%20by%20the%20app%20promoters%20has%20been%20invested%20in%20many%20companies%2C%20shell%20companies%2C%20stock%20market%20and%20crypto%20currency%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20betting%20platform%20called%20Sky%20Exchange%20was%20being%20run%20by%20Hari%20Shankar%20Tibrewal%2C%20who%20was%20associated%20with%20the%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20and%20the%20ED%20has%20attached%20his%20assets%20worth%20around%20Rs%20580%20crore%2C%20the%20FIR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20illegal%20act%20of%20online%20betting%2C%20the%20promoters%20of%20Mahadev%20Book%20App%20had%20given%20huge%20protection%20money%20to%20various%20police%20and%20administrative%20officers%20and%20influential%20political%20persons%2C%20it%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHawala%20operators%20were%20used%20for%20the%20arrangement%20and%20distribution%20of%20the%20protection%20money%20and%20police%20officers%2Femployees%20were%20also%20used%20as%20couriers%20for%20the%20purpose%2C%20the%20FIR%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20police%2C%20administrative%20officers%20and%20influential%20political%20persons%20have%20misused%20their%20positions%20and%20acquired%20illegal%20assets%20in%20the%20form%20of%20protection%20money.%20Provisional%20attachment%20of%20many%20immovable%20properties%20has%20been%20done%20by%20the%20ED%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leaders%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20targeted%20Baghel%20over%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20case%20during%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20polls%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaghel%20had%20termed%20the%20ED's%20action%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20the%20federal%20agency%20of%20acting%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20masters%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20arrested%20nine%20persons%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20filed%20two%20chargesheets%20in%20the%20case%20till%20now%20in%20Raipur%20court%2C%20including%20against%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal.%20It%20had%20earlier%20conducted%20multiple%20raids%20in%20connection%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOperations%20of%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20are%20being%20run%20from%20Dubai%20and%20it%20operates%20by%20franchising%20panel%2Fbranches%20to%20their%20known%20associates%20on%2070-30%20per%20cent%20profit%20ratio%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ED%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20promoters%20of%20MOB%20are%20also%20partners%2Fpromoters%20in%20multiple%20such%20online%20betting%20books%20like%20Reddy%20Anna%2C%20Fairplay%2C%20etc%20and%20large-scale%20hawala%20operations%20are%20done%20to%20siphon%20off%20the%20proceeds%20of%20betting%20proceeds%20to%20off-shore%20accounts%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710672720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fs74boj2o_bhupesh-baghel-pti_625x300_16_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.c