t%20the%20world%20had%20witnessed%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-06-03%2Findia-s-bitterly-fought-poll-becomes-the-world-s-most-expensive%5C%22%3Estudy%20cited%20by%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-06-03%2Findia-s-bitterly-fought-poll-becomes-the-world-s-most-expensive%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0more%20expensive%20than%20the%20one%20held%20in%20the%20US%20which%20elected%20Donald%20Trump%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20amount%20the%20BJP%20has%20recorded%20as%20receiving%20in%20FY%202017-18%20is%20Rs%202%2C10%2C00%2C02%2C000.%C2%A0In%20FY%202018-19%20it%20got%20Rs%2014%2C50%2C89%2C05%2C000.%C2%A0In%20FY%202019-20%20it%20got%20Rs%2025%2C55%2C00%2C01%2C000.%C2%A0In%20FY%202020-21%20it%20got%20Rs%2022%2C38%2C50%2C000.%C2%A0In%20FY%202021-22%20it%20got%20Rs%2010%2C33%2C70%2C00%2C000.%C2%A0In%20FY%202022-23%20it%20got%20Rs%202%2C94%2C14%2C99%2C000.%C2%A0In%20FY%202023-24%20(until%20September%2030%2C%202023)%20it%20got%20Rs%204%2C21%2C27%2C51%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710672359000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-got-approx-rs-3962-crore-in-electoral-bonds-before-2019-polls-sealed-cover-data-unveiled-by-ec%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20the%20amount%20it%20had%20available%20to%20spend%20on%20the%20last%20general%20election%2C%20exactly%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20funding%20from%20other%20sources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-got-approx-rs-3962-crore-in-electoral-bonds-before-2019-polls-sealed-cover-data-unveiled-by-ec%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trouble%20In%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Team%3F%20Pacer%20Reveals%20'Culture%20Of%20Insecurity'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20fast%20bowler%20Naseem%20Shah%20has%20come%20out%20in%20the%20open%20about%20the%20culture%20of%20insecurity%20in%20the%20national%20side%2C%20saying%20senior%20players%20are%20afraid%20of%20taking%20breaks%20to%20rest%20their%20bodies%2C%20fearing%20replacement%20by%20younger%20players.%20Shah%2C%20who%20was%20ruled%20out%20of%20the%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20in%20India%20last%20year%20due%20to%20a%20shoulder%20problem%2C%20added%20that%20even%20he%20was%20afraid%20about%20losing%20his%20place%20in%20the%20side%20due%20to%20the%20injury.%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20the%20main%20players%20are%20afraid%20of%20giving%20their%20bodies%20rest%20even%20when%20they%20know%20they%20need%20a%20break%20because%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20culture%20is%20such%20that%20if%20a%20new%20player%20comes%20in%20and%20performs%20in%20a%20match%20or%20two%2C%20you%20don't%20know%20if%20he%20will%20replace%20you%20permanently%20in%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20told%20Cricwick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20fear%20does%20not%20allow%20players%20to%20rest%20because%20you%20are%20scared%20your%20careers%20could%20end%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20young%20bowler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseem%20said%20there%20was%20a%20need%20for%20clarity%20and%20better%20communication%20between%20senior%20players%2C%20team%20management%2C%20selectors%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20other%20countries%2C%20if%20a%20main%20player%20is%20given%20a%20break%20he%20is%20assured%20he%20will%20not%20be%20dropped%20in%20case%20his%20replacement%20comes%20in%20and%20performs%20in%20a%20match%20or%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20a%20player's%20commitment%20in%20Pakistan%20is%20questioned%20if%20he%20says%20he%20is%20not%20feeling%20100%20per%20cent%20or%20his%20body%20needs%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bowler%20felt%20that%20the%20physio%2C%20bowling%20coach%20and%20trainer%20should%20decide%20before%20a%20series%20how%20many%20matches%20a%20player%20should%20play%2C%20which%20will%20eliminate%20insecurity%20and%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20who%20returned%20to%20action%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20Super%20League%20after%20missing%20a%20few%20matches%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20tours%20of%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20because%20of%20the%20shoulder%20injury%2C%20said%20if%20the%20players%20have%20clarity%2C%20there%20will%20fewer%20long-term%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20he%20initially%20thought%20his%20injury%20wasn't%20too%20serious%20after%20he%20hurt%20his%20shoulder%20while%20saving%20a%20boundary%20against%20Bangladesh%20and%20walked%20off%20the%20pitch%20in%20the%20subsequent%20tie%20against%20India%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20stiffness%20in%20my%20shoulder%20but%20after%20warm-ups%20it%20would%20get%20better%20and%20I%20played%20through%20it.%20But%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20I%20had%20a%20tear%20and%20felt%20something%20tearing%20inside%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20said%20that%20following%20the%20surgery%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20he%20was%20told%20that%20the%20tear%20was%20about%20%26quot%3B4%20or%205%20centimetres%26quot%3B%20long.%20PTI%20Cor%20AM%20AM%20AM%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710672240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjaks83k8_pakistan-cricket-team-afp_625x300_17_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ftrouble-in-pakistan-cricket-team-young-fast-bowler-reveals-culture-of-insecurity-5255881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Naseem%20Shah%20has%20come%20out%20in%20the%20open%20about%20the%20culture%20of%20insecurity%20in%20the%20national%20side%2C%20saying%20senior%20players%20are%20afraid%20of%20taking%20breaks%20to%20rest%20their%20bodies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky%20Kaushal%20on%20'Sam%20Bahadur'%20and%20'Animal'%20clash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710671641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108563210%2Cimgsize-66192.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-on-sam-bahadur-and-animal-clash-i-knew-it-was-a-challenging-test-from-the-start%2Farticleshow%2F108563184.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108563184.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVicky%20Kaushal's%20performance%20as%20Sam%20Manekshaw%20in%20'Sam%20Bahadur'%20received%20praise%20despite%20competition%20from%20Ranbir%20Kapoor's%20'Animal.'%20The%20success%20of%20the%20film%20relied%20on%20emotional%20audience%20resonance%2C%20with%20continued%20screenings%20in%20January%20showcasing%20sustained%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EC%20changes%20counting%20date%20of%20Arunachal%2C%20Sikkim%20to%20June%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710671313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108563123%2Cimgsize-818405.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fassembly-polls-ec-changes-counting-date-of-arunachal-pradesh-sikkim-to-june-2%2Farticleshow%2F108563093.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20moved%20the%20counting%20date%20for%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Sikkim%20from%20June%204%20to%20June%202.%20The%20states'%20schedules%20for%20Parliamentary%20constituencies%20have%20not%20changed.%20In%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20EC%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BECI%20is%20to%20conduct%20election%20to%20Legislative%20Assemblies%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Sikkim%20before%20the%20cessation%20of%20their%20terms...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fresh%20Data%20On%20Funding%20To%20Political%20Parties%20Through%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Released%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20today%20released%20data%20received%20from%20political%20parties%20on%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20which%20it%20had%20given%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20sealed%20covers.%20These%20details%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20for%20the%20period%20before%20April%2012%2C%202019.%20Electoral%20bond%20details%20after%20this%20date%20was%20made%20public%20by%20the%20EC%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20Registry%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20returned%20physical%20copies%20along%20with%20a%20digitised%20record%20of%20the%20same%20in%20a%20pen%20drive%20in%20sealed%20cover.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20today%20uploaded%20the%20data%20received%20in%20digitised%20form%20from%20the%20registry%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20on%20its%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20EC%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20released%20the%20data%20a%20day%20after%20it%20announced%20the%20dates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20in%20seven%20phases%20from%20April%2019%20to%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20documents%20released%20by%20the%20EC%20only%20show%20raw%20data%20of%20the%20date%20of%20the%20bonds%2C%20denominations%2C%20number%20of%20bonds%2C%20issuing%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20(SBI)%20branch%2C%20date%20of%20receipt%2C%20and%20date%20of%20credit.%20It%20does%20not%20disclose%20the%20unique%20numbers%20of%20the%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20written%20to%20SBI%20asking%20for%20the%20unique%20numbers%20of%20the%20bonds%20so%20that%20the%20party%20can%20comply%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20directions.%20The%20BJP%20has%20not%20given%20any%20such%20request%20to%20SBI%2C%20but%20has%20given%20raw%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20said%20it%20hasn't%20got%20any%20donation%20via%20electoral%20bonds.%20The%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20or%20CPI(M)%2C%20said%20it%20too%20didn't%20get%20donations%20via%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20DMK%20received%20Rs%20656.5%20crore%20through%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20including%20Rs%20509%20crore%20from%20lottery%20king%20Santiago%20Martin's%20Future%20Gaming%2C%20the%20EC%20data%20shows%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20said%20it%20will%20release%20raw%20data%20given%20by%20SBI%20to%20the%20EC.%20The%20Congress's%20Goa%20unit%20said%20it%20got%20a%20donation%20of%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20from%20VM%20Salgaocar%2C%20a%20company%20based%20in%20Vasco%20da%20Gama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20Tripura%20unit%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party's%20West%20Bengal%20unit%20said%20they%20have%20not%20got%20any%20donation%20via%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(TRS)%2C%20now%20known%20as%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20got%20Rs%20230.65%20crore%20in%20bonds%20from%202018%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka's%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20or%20JD(S)%2C%20said%20Embassy%20Group%2C%20Infosys%2C%20and%20Biocon%20are%20among%20their%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElectoral%20bonds%20have%20been%20a%20key%20method%20of%20political%20funding%2C%20allowing%20donors%20to%20give%20anonymously%20through%20certificates%20purchased%20from%20SBI.%20But%20last%20month%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20struck%20down%20the%20scheme%20as%20unconstitutional%2C%20saying%20it%20violated%20the%20right%20of%20voters%20to%20know%20who%20was%20financing%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20received%20slightly%20less%20than%2048%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20election%20bonds%20cashed%20by%20parties%20up%20to%20March%202023.%20In%20the%20same%20timeframe%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20by%20contrast%20received%2011%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20half%20of%20all%20donations%20received%20by%20political%20parties%20since%202018%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20according%20to%20the%20advocacy%20group%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR).%20The%20data%20release%20still%20does%20not%20map%20electoral%20bond%20buyers%20to%20recipients%2C%20leaving%20it%20unclear%20which%20individual%20and%20corporate%20donors%20were%20funding%20which%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710671280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F2074em5g_rajasthan-assembly-elections-_625x300_11_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoll-panel-releases-fresh-data-on-funding-to-political-parties-through-electoral-bonds-5255720%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission%20today%20released%20data%20received%20from%20political%20parties%20on%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20which%20it%20had%20given%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20sealed%20covers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoll-panel-releases-fresh-data-on-funding-to-political-parties-through-electoral-bonds-5255720%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoll-panel-releases-fresh-data-on-funding-to-political-parties-through-electoral-bonds-5255720%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpoll-panel-releases-fresh-data-on-funding-to-political-parties-through-electoral-bonds-5255720%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22ti