%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68589594.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elvish%20Yadav%20arrested%20by%20Noida%20Police%20in%20snake%20venom%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710670344000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108562817%2Cimgsize-43984.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fbigg-boss-ott-winner-elvish-yadav-arrested-by-noida-police-in-snake-venom-case%2Farticleshow%2F108562842.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elvish%20Yadav%2C%20the%20winner%20of%20Bigg%20Boss%20OTT%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Noida%20Police%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20snake%20venom%20case.%20For%20further%20details%20and%20updates%20on%20this%20development.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flipkart%20To%20Pay%20Man%20Rs%2010%2C000%20For%20Harassment%20After%20Cancelled%20iPhone%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20consumer%20disputes%20redressal%20commission%20here%20found%20Flipkart%20guilty%20of%20adopting%20unfair%20trade%20practices%20and%20ordered%20it%20to%20pay%20a%20customer%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20the%20mental%20harassment%20he%20suffered%20after%20it%20cancelled%20his%20iPhone%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20was%20intentional%20to%20make%20extra%20profit%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20a%20deficiency%20in%20service%20and%20unfair%20and%20restrictive%20trade%20practice%20adopted%20by%20the%20online%20platform%2C%20said%20the%20District%20Consumer%20Disputes%20Redressal%20Commission%2C%20Central%20Mumbai%2C%20in%20the%20order%20passed%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20detailed%20order%20was%20available%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20noted%20that%20though%20the%20customer%20had%20received%20a%20refund%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20be%20compensated%20for%20the%20mental%20harassment%20and%20agony%20he%20suffered%20because%20of%20the%20unilateral%20cancellation%20of%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20complainant%2C%20a%20Dadar%20resident%2C%20he%20ordered%20an%20iPhone%20from%20Flipkart%20on%20July%2C%2010%202022%20and%20paid%20Rs%2039%2C628%20using%20his%20credit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20phone%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20delivered%20on%20July%2012%2C%20but%20six%20days%20later%20he%20received%20an%20SMS%20from%20the%20e-commerce%20company%20that%20his%20order%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20the%20company%20told%20him%20that%20their%20Ekart%20delivery%20boy%20had%20made%20several%20attempts%20to%20deliver%20the%20product%20but%20the%20complainant%20was%20unavailable%20and%20hence%2C%20the%20order%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cancellation%20has%20not%20only%20caused%20loss%2C%20and%20mental%20harassment%20but%20also%20subjected%20him%20to%20online%20fraud%2C%20the%20complainant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlipkart's%20delivery%20partner%2C%20Ekart%20Logistics%2C%20was%20also%20a%20party%20to%20the%20complaint%20but%20the%20commission%20held%20that%20it%20is%20a%20delivery%20partner%20and%20there%20is%20no%20consumer%20and%20service%20provider%20relationship%20between%20the%20complainant%20and%20the%20logistics%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlipkart%2C%20in%20its%20written%20response%2C%20said%20the%20complainant%20had%20mistakenly%20taken%20it%20as%20the%20seller%20of%20the%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20merely%20operates%20as%20an%20online%20platform%20as%20an%20intermediary%2C%20and%20all%20the%20products%20on%20the%20platform%20are%20sold%20and%20supplied%20by%20independent%20third-party%20sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seller%20in%20this%20case%20was%20International%20Value%20Retail%20Private%20Limited%2C%20and%20Flipkart%20had%20no%20role%20to%20play%20in%20the%20entire%20transaction%20entered%20between%20the%20complainant%20and%20the%20seller%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20claimed%20that%20it%20informed%20the%20seller%20of%20the%20complainant's%20grievance%2C%20the%20latter%20said%20the%20delivery%20person%20had%20made%20several%20attempts%20to%20deliver%20the%20product%20to%20the%20address%20but%20the%20complainant%20was%20unavailable%20and%20hence%2C%20the%20order%20was%20cancelled%20by%20the%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20has%20been%20refunded%20and%20the%20dispute%20exists%20only%20between%20the%20complainant%20and%20the%20seller%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20cause%20of%20action%20against%20Flipkart%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20commission%2C%20noted%20that%20the%20order%20was%20%26quot%3Bunilaterally%20cancelled%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20e-commerce%20company%20that%20too%20when%20the%20complainant%20was%20constantly%20in%20touch%20with%20it%20and%20was%20assured%20that%20his%20concern%20was%20being%20looked%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20Flipkart%20had%20not%20produced%20any%20proof%20about%20multiple%20attempts%20of%20service%20by%20it%20or%20by%20the%20seller%20as%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20noted%20that%20Flipkart%20has%20admitted%20that%20the%20order%20was%20cancelled%20and%20the%20complainant%20was%20asked%20to%20place%20a%20fresh%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20adds%20weight%20to%20the%20complainant's%20case%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20said%20product%20had%20increased%20by%20around%20Rs%207%2C000%20and%20hence%20the%20order%20was%20cancelled%20and%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20place%20a%20fresh%20order%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20pointed%20out%20that%20Flipkart%20had%20done%20this%20intentionally%20to%20make%20extra%20profit%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20a%20deficiency%20in%20service%20and%20unfair%20and%20restrictive%20trade%20practices%20adopted%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20the%20complainant%20has%20received%20the%20refund%2C%20he%20needs%20to%20be%20compensated%20for%20the%20mental%20harassment%20and%20agony%20suffered%20by%20him%20due%20to%20the%20unilateral%20cancellation%20of%20his%20order%20by%20Flipkart%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20ordered%20Flipkart%20to%20pay%20Rs%2010%2C000%20towards%20compensation%20for%20the%20mental%20harassment%20and%20agony%20suffered%20by%20the%20complainant%20and%20Rs%203%2C000%20towards%20the%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710670320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fqk443pro_flipkart_625x300_01_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflipkart-to-pay-man-rs-10-000-for-harassment-after-cancelled-iphone-order-5255924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20consumer%20disputes%20redressal%20commission%20here%20found%20Flipkart%20guilty%20of%20adopting%20unfair%20trade%20practices%20and%20ordered%20it%20to%20pay%20a%20customer%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20the%20mental%20harassment%20he%20suffered%20after%20it%20cancelled%20his%20iPhone%20order.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflipkart-to-pay-man-rs-10-000-for-harassment-after-cancelled-iphone-order-5255924%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflipkart-to-pay-man-rs-10-000-for-harassment-after-cancelled-iphone-order-5255924%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fflipkart-to-pay-man-rs-10-000-for-harassment-after-cancelled-iphone-order-5255924%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20Orders%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20File%20Report%20on%20Policeman%20Who%20Kicked%20Muslims%20at%20Prayer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09110035%2F108329889.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20Delhi%20court%20on%20March%2016%2C%20Saturday%2C%20called%20for%20a%20report%20on%20the%20incident%20last%20Friday%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Inderlok%20area%2C%20where%20a%20policeman%20kicking%20Muslim%20persons%20who%20were%20seen%20offering%20namaz%20in%20a%20public%20space%20created%20an%20uproar.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Flawyer-delhi-police-kicking-namaz-magistrate-dcp-report%23%3A~%3Atext%3DA%2520Delhi%2520court%2520on%2520Saturday%2CInspector%2520Manoj%2520Tomar%2520and%2520anr%255D.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20concerned%20District%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20was%20asked%20to%20file%20a%20report%20regarding%20the%20recent%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20in%20Tis%20Hazari%20has%20ordered%20that%20an%20action-taken%20report%20be%20submitted%20by%20May%201%2C%20the%20date%20when%20the%20matter%20is%20set%20to%20be%20heard%20next.%20Sub-inspector%20(SI)%20Manoj%20Tomar%20was%20seen%20kicking%20those%20offering%20prayers%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Inderlok%20area%20near%20the%20Makki%20Jama%20Masjid.%20The%20viral%20video%20generated%20outrage%20and%20prompted%20a%20suspension%20on%20March%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20SI%20Tomar%20can%20be%20%E2%80%9Cseen%20kicking%20and%20shoving%20people%20praying%20on%20the%20road%2C%20and%20even%20shouting%20and%20stepping%20on%20the%20prayer%20mats%20used%20by%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20parallel%20misinformation%20online%2C%20that%20a%20mob%20in%20the%20area%20had%20attacked%20the%20policeman.%20The%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDcpNorthDelhi%2Fstatus%2F1766861664933048814%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Edebunked%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Tomar%20now%20faces%20disciplinary%20action.%20%E2%80%9CA%20departmental%20inquiry%20has%20been%20initiated%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20NDTV%20reported%20citing%20police%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist%20and%20Magsaysay%20award%20winner%20Ravish%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdont-hide-your-communal-prejudice-under-the-cloak-of-protecting-our-roads%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20not%20about%20not%20causing%20traffic%20jams.%20%E2%80%9CCan%20a%20blanket%20ban%20be%20imposed%20on%20all%20types%20of%20religious%20events%20on%20roads%3F%20That%20will%20more%20adversely%20affect%20hundreds%20of%20religious%20processions%20and%20events%20of%20Hindus%20which%20go%20on%20for%20several%20days.%20The%20desire%20to%20impose%20a%20ban%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20the%20demand%20for%20improved%20management%20of%20roads.%20But%20it%20only%20reflects%20the%20frustration%20towards%20a%20community%20and%20an%20insistence%20on%20spewing%20poison.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20not%20with%20namaz%20being%20offered%20on%20the%20road.%20How%20does%20it%20affect%20someone%20if%20a%20person%20offers%20namaz%20on%20a%20moving%20train%3F%20People%20have%20been%20doing%20so%20for%20ages%20and%20no%20one%20cared.%20But%20now%20a%20video%20is%20recorded%20which%20becomes%20the%20subject%20of%20debate%20on%20TV%20and%20the%C2%A0namazi%C2%A0is%20arrested.%20If%20someone%20offers%20it%20in%20the%20mall%2C%20a%20video%20is%20shot%2C%20hatred%20is%20spread%20over%20it%20and%20an%20uproar%20is%20created.%20Does%20offering%20namaz%20at%20a%20corner%20inside%20a%20mall%20or%20a%20coaching%20centre%20also%20lead%20to%20traffic%20jam%3F%20Recently%2C%20we%20saw%20passengers%20singing%20bhajans%20and%20raising%20slogans%20of%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20in%20planes%20carrying%20visitors%20to%20Ram%20temple.%20Was%20there%20uproar%20then%3F%20People%20have%20been%20doing%20bhajan-kirtan%20on%20trains%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20This%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20our%20train%20journeys.%20To%20ask%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20it%20sounds%20strange.%20Then%20people%20should%20not%20even%20play%C2%A0antakshari%C2%A0on%20the%20train.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710670252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09110035%2F108329889.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcourt-orders-delhi-police-to-file-report-on-policeman-who-kicked-muslims-at-prayer%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20a%20sub-inspector%20was%20seen%20kicking%20muslims%20offering%20Friday%20prayers%20on%20a%20road%20in%20Inderlok%20area.%20The%2034%20second%20video%20that%20later%20went%20viral%20and%20led%20to%20the%20policeman%E2%80%99s%20suspension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcourt-orders-delhi-police-to-file-report-on-policeman-who-kicked-muslims-at-prayer%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gujarat%20University%20Plans%20%26quot%3BSensitivity%26quot%3B%20Drill%20For%20Foreigners%20Amid%20Namaz%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujarat%20University%20will%20be%20holding%20orientation%20sessions%20for%20its%20overseas%20students%20to%20train%20them%20in%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20sensitivity%26quot%3B%2C%20Vice-Chancellor%20Dr%20Neerja%20A%20Gupta%20said%20today%2C%20hours%20after%20a%20mob%20stormed%20a%20hostel%20and%20attacked%20foreign%20students%20for%20offering%20namaz%20inside%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20international%20students%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20mob%20attack%20last%20night.%20Police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20and%20formed%20nine%20teams%20to%20search%20for%20those%20in%20the%20mob.%20Ahmedabad%20police%20commissioner%20GS%20Malik%20has%20said%20strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20incident.%20Gujarat%20University%20has%20about%20300%20overseas%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVice-Chancellor%20Dr%20Gupta%20told%20the%20media%20that%20there%20was%20some%20tension%20between%20those%20in%20the%20mob%20and%20some%20overseas%20students%2C%20and%20yesterday's%20events%20led%20to%20an%20escalation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20is%20under%20police%20investigation%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Gupta%20said%20that%20since%20these%20students%20are%20from%20overseas%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20trained%20in%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20sensitivity%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20foreign%20students%20and%20when%20you%20go%20abroad%2C%20you%20must%20learn%20cultural%20sensitivity.%20These%20students%20need%20an%20orientation.%20We%20will%20sit%20with%20them%2C%20provide%20cultural%20orientation%20and%20discuss%20how%20to%20strengthen%20their%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20international%20students%20have%20said%20there%20is%20no%20mosque%20on%20the%20campus%2C%20so%20they%20had%20gathered%20inside%20the%20hostel%20to%20offer%20taraweeh%20-%20a%20namaz%20offered%20at%20night%20during%20Ramadan.%20Soon%20after%2C%20a%20mob%20armed%20with%20sticks%20and%20knives%20stormed%20the%20hostel%2C%20attacked%20them%20and%20vandalised%20their%20rooms%2C%20the%20students%20have%20alleged.%20The%20students%20have%20said%20the%20security%20guard%20of%20the%20hostel%20tried%20to%20stop%20the%20mob%2C%20but%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%20from%20Afghanistan%20said%20people%20in%20the%20mob%20raised%20slogans%20and%20asked%20them%20who%20had%20allowed%20them%20to%20offer%20namaz%20in%20the%20hostel.%20%26quot%3BThey%20attacked%20us%20inside%20the%20rooms%20too.%20They%20broke%20laptops%2C%20phones%20and%20damaged%20bikes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20said%20the%20five%20injured%20students%20include%20one%20each%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Turkmenistan%20and%20two%20from%20African%20countries.%20The%20injured%20students%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20informed%20the%20embassies%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20videos%2C%20a%20youngster%20in%20the%20mob%20is%20heard%20asking%20a%20security%20guard%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20they%20offering%20namaz%2C%20is%20this%20the%20place%3F%26quot%3B%20At%20this%20point%2C%20a%20student%20screams%2C%20approaches%20the%20youngster%20and%20attacks%20him.%20Some%20users%20on%20social%20media%20have%20claimed%20this%20triggered%20the%20mob%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710670140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc220d0r8_gujarat-university-mob-_625x300_17_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-university-mob-attack-gujarat-university-plans-sensitivity-drill-for-foreigners-amid-namaz-row-5255676%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gujarat%20University%20will%20be%20holding%20orientation%20sessions%20for%20its%20overseas%20students%20to%20train%20them%20in%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20sensitivity%26quot%3B%2C%20Vice-Chancellor%20Dr%20Neerja%20A%20Gupta%20said%2C%20hours%20after%20a%20mob%20stormed%20a%20hostel%20and%20attacked%20foreign%20students%20for%20offering%20namaz%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-university-mob-attack-gujarat-university-plans-sensitivity-drill-for-foreigners-amid-namaz-row-5255676%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-university-mob-attack-gujarat-university-plans-sensitivity-drill-for-foreigners-amid-namaz-row-5255676%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-university-mob-attack-gujarat-university-plans-sensitivity-drill-for-foreigners-amid-namaz-row-5255676%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sham%20Kaushal%20on%20working%20with%20son%20Vicky%20in%20Dunki%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17106700350