C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20both%20the%20man%20and%20the%20woman%20ran%20off%20in%20separate%20directions.%20The%20two%20were%20allegedly%20being%20chased%20while%20strolling%20in%20the%20Demanovska%20Valley%2C%20according%20to%20Slovak%20officials.%20A%20search%20dog%20discovered%20the%20woman's%20body%20shortly%20after%20her%20partner%20sought%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20officials%20discovered%20her%20body%2C%20the%20bear%20was%20close%20and%20had%20to%20be%20driven%20away%20by%20repeated%20bullets%20fired%20by%20the%20Mountain%20Rescue%20Service.%20However%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20whether%20the%20woman%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20wild%20animal%20or%20died%20due%20to%20a%20fall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20brown%20bears%20are%20widespread%20throughout%20eastern%20and%20northeastern%20Europe%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20found%20in%20the%20Carpathian%20Mountains%2C%20which%20cut%20through%20Romania%2C%20Slovakia%2C%20Poland%2C%20and%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20reportedly%201%2C275%20bears%20in%20Slovakia%2C%20according%20to%20researchers.%20The%20nation%20has%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20bear%20attacks%2C%20with%20one%20of%20the%20deadliest%20in%20over%20a%20century%20occurring%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country's%20brown%20bear%20population%20is%20a%20contentious%20political%20issue%20since%20Slovakia's%20recently%20elected%20populist%20nationalist%20government%20wishes%20less%20environmental%20protection%20from%20the%20European%20Union%20for%20wolves%20and%20bears%2C%20among%20other%20predators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnvironmental%20organisations%2C%20including%20the%20Slovak%20Wildlife%20Society%20and%20the%20World%20Wildlife%20Fund%2C%20have%20opposed%20any%20proposals%20to%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20brown%20bears%20in%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710665400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F9rrvu9u_bear_625x300_17_March_24.jpeg