e%20tea-tray%20sized%20cards%20carry%20at%20least%20half-a-dozen%20sub-invites%20that%20list%20these%20fringe%20functions%3A%20ring%20ceremony%2C%20cocktails%2C%20%3Cem%3Emehendi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Esangeet%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20god%20knows%20what%20else%20besides.%20If%20you%20look%20hard%2C%20you%20may%20spot%20the%20name%20of%20the%20couple%2C%20and%20move%20on%20to%20the%20list%20of%20parents%2C%20grandparents%2C%20great-grandparents%2C%20cousins%2C%20uncles%20and%20aunts%2C%20siblings%20(married%20or%20otherwise)%20and%20around%20a%20dozen%20nephews%20and%20nieces%20as%20folks%20that%20await%20your%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Cem%3Edarshanabhilashi%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20merciful%20presence%20(%3Cem%3Ekripakangshi%3C%2Fem%3E)%20at%20some%20half%20a%20dozen%20festivities%20associated%20with%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20just%20as%20an%20editor%20mistook%20his%20team%20for%20a%20batch%20of%20serfs%20at%20his%20(and%20rarely%2C%20her)%20beck%20and%20call%2C%20family%20elders%20too%20feel%20they%20know%20all%20about%20eminently%20marriageable%20young%20in%20their%20community.%20So%20like%20writing%20the%20daily%20editorials%20(which%20few%20read)%2C%20matchmaking%20firmly%20excluded%20the%20young%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20entirely%20by%20seniors%20with%20some%20help%20from%20a%20trusted%20family%20astrologer%20and%20the%20family%20barber%20(since%20he%20regularly%20shaved%20and%20massaged%20all%20eligible%20and%20non-eligible%20males%20in%20the%20area%20and%20was%20an%20invaluable%20repository%20of%20details%20regarding%20their%20physical%20fitness%20including%20the%20state%20of%20their%20hair%2C%20teeth%2C%20eyes%20etc).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20marriageable%20ones%20being%20spied%20upon%20by%20trusted%20family%20friends%2C%20I%20recall%20Ama%20once%20dictating%20to%20me%20one%20such%20letter%20of%20%E2%80%9Cobservations%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20non-resident%20relative%20regarding%20a%20particular%20young%20man%20from%20our%20area%20who%20had%20been%C2%A0%20recommended%20by%20someone%20as%20an%20eligible%20bachelor%20to%20the%20parents%20of%20some%20unnamed%20marriageable%20girl%20from%20our%20vast%20clan.%20After%20the%20routine%20%E2%80%9CMay%20Peace%20be%20upon%20you%2C%20worthy%20of%20all%20high%20titles%2C%20Shri%20so%20and%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ama%20came%20to%20the%20point%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20you%20had%20asked%20me%20to%20check%20on%20Shri%20So%20and%20So%E2%80%99s%20Chiranjivi%20son%2C%20I%20note%20below%20my%20findings.%20Of%20course%20the%20young%20man%20has%20an%20impeccable%20lineage%20and%20counting%20seven%20generations%20from%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20side%20and%20five%20from%20the%20mother%E2%80%99s%2C%20one%20could%20detect%20no%20blood%20relationship%2C%20so%20that%20particular%20aspect%20too%20is%20taken%20care%20of.%20The%20young%20man%20is%20said%20moreover%20to%20be%20of%20a%20most%20obedient%20son%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20and%20a%20good%20earner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhysically%20he%20is%20somewhat%20dark%20of%20mien%20and%20according%20to%20Ramnath%20Baaji%2C%20the%20barber%2C%20has%20a%20cast%20in%20one%20eye.%20As%20I%20observed%20his%20gait%20from%20my%20house%2C%20his%20left%20leg%20seemed%20a%20bit%20shorter%20than%20his%20right.%20Upon%20enquiry%20I%20learnt%20that%20his%20mother%2C%20while%20she%20was%20expecting%20him%2C%20had%20stepped%20out%20to%20see%20an%20eclipse%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20aforementioned%20anomaly.%20However%2C%20as%20a%20groom%20he%20is%20alright%E2%80%A6Don%E2%80%99t%20just%20gape%20at%20me%2C%20write%20girl%2C%20write!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20command%20was%20barked%20out%20to%20me.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20Ama%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20remonstrated%2C%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20naming%20all%20those%20awful%20physical%20defects%2C%20how%20can%20you%20say%20he%20is%20okay%20as%20a%20groom%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShut%20up!%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ama.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20are%20we%20to%20find%20fault%20in%20another%E2%80%99s%C2%A0son%3F%20And%20in%20any%20case%2C%20if%20finally%20the%20parents%20decide%20to%20marry%20their%20girl%20to%20the%20bloke%2C%20can%20you%20imagine%20how%20foolish%20that%20can%20make%20me%20look%3F%20%3Cem%3EShaadi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20girl%2C%20is%20like%20a%20sweet%20laddoo.%20You%20eat%20it%20and%20feel%20sorry%2C%20but%20if%20you%20do%20not%20eat%20it%20you%20may%20feel%20sorrier%20still!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710661449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F17130717%2FGHpnMcXWsAA63hy.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthe-big-fat-indian-wedding%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indians%20of%20all%20classes%20are%20by%20and%20large%20still%20wary%2C%20if%20not%20totally%20outraged%2C%20by%20the%20thought%20of%20their%20young%20choosing%20their%20own%20partners%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20something%20as%20tawdry%20as%20love.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthe-big-fat-indian-wedding%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20children%20exposed%20to%20risks%20of%20violent%20and%20self-harm%20content%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710661436000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108560664%2Cimgsize-1606169.