ofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fonly-few-people-know-kate-middletons-absence-raises-concern-among-staff%2Famp_articleshow%2F108559982.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Panel%20of%20Five%20Scholars%20Will%20Be%20Monitoring%20India's%202024%20Elections%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20Indian%20citizens%20will%20elect%20their%20political%20representatives%20for%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20upcoming%20months%2C%20five%20scholars%20based%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20have%20come%20together%20to%20form%20a%20dedicated%20panel%20to%20monitor%20the%20polls.%20The%20group%20plans%20to%20point%20out%20possible%20violations%20in%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20and%20whether%20there%20is%20an%20erosion%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20political%20parties%20and%20voters%20from%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20from%20an%20understanding%20that%20the%20use%20of%20money%2C%20muscle%20and%20institutional%20corruption%20over%20the%20years%20may%20have%20compromised%20the%20conduct%20of%20a%20totally%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20in%20India%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20democracies%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20members%20of%20the%20panel%20believe%20that%20a%20civil%20society%20initiative%20like%20theirs%20may%20raise%20concerns%20of%20the%20citizens%20more%20pertinently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndependent%20panel%20for%20monitoring%20Indian%20elections%20%E2%80%93%202024%E2%80%9D%20are%20Neera%20Chandhoke%20(National%20Fellow%20at%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Social%20Science%20Research%2C%20and%20retd.%20Professor%2C%20Delhi%20University%2C%20India)%2C%20Dr%20Thomas%20Daffern%20(philosopher%20and%20historian%3B%20chairman%20of%20World%20Intellectuals%20Wisdom%20Forum%3B%20Director%2C%20International%20Institute%20of%20Peace%20Studies%20and%20Global%20Philosophy%20(France%20and%20UK)%3B%20Convenor%2C%20Commonwealth%20Interfaith%20Network)%2C%20Sakhawat%20Hossain%20(former%20election%20commissioner%20of%20Bangladesh)%2C%20Dr%20Harish%20Karnick%20(former%20professor%2C%20IIT%2C%20Kanpur)%2C%20Dr%20Sebastian%20Morris%20(former%20professor%2C%20IIM%2C%20Ahmedabad)%20and%20Professor%20Rahul%20Mukherji%20(Professor%20%26amp%3B%20Chair%2C%20Modern%20Politics%20of%20South%20Asia%2C%20South%20Asia%20Institute%2C%20Heidelberg%20University%2C%20Germany).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%2C%20in%20a%20pre-election%20report%2C%20said%20that%20the%20idea%20to%20form%20a%20group%20came%20from%20concerns%20raised%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%20regarding%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccredibility%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20to%20ensure%20a%20level-playing%20field%20between%20political%20parties%2C%20and%20address%20grievances%20of%20stakeholders%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20970%20million%20Indian%20voters%20will%20cast%20their%20votes%20in%20April-May%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCitizens%20groups%20from%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20are%20voicing%20their%20worry%20that%20elections%20will%20not%20be%20free%20and%20fair%2C%20hence%20not%20genuine.%20In%20specific%20regions%2C%20there%20is%20also%20anguish%20about%20the%20likely%20denial%20of%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20of%20exclusion%20of%20vulnerable%20groups%20from%20voting%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Csecuring%20the%20will%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Censuring%20a%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D%20are%20two%20cornerstones%20of%20a%20representative%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20flagged%20the%20following%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20Indian%20media%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20%E2%80%93%2030%20million%20Muslim%20voters%2C%2040%20million%20voters%2C%20and%20a%20number%20of%20Christians%20were%20missing%20from%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20of%202019.%20The%20report%20also%20raised%20its%20protest%20against%20the%20ECI%20and%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20conduct%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20since%202018.%20It%20said%20that%20the%20ECI%20marked%20almost%20one%20lakh%20voters%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdoubtful%20voters%20or%20D-voters%E2%80%9D%2C%20most%20of%20them%20Bengali-speaking%20Muslims%2C%20risking%20their%20right%20to%20vote.%20It%20said%20that%20that%20in%20states%20in%20territories%20like%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Assam%2C%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20has%20disadvantaged%20Muslims%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20their%20proportionate%20representation%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP-led%20central%20government%20has%20systematically%20targeted%20opposition%20parties%2C%20whilst%20it%20has%20sought%20to%20strengthen%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20hold.%20Central%20investigating%20agencies%20have%20initiated%20a%20slew%20of%20criminal%20cases%20against%20opposition%20leaders.%20According%20to%20one%20report%2C%2090%25%20of%20all%20cases%20against%20political%20parties%20since%202014%2C%20by%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20have%20been%20against%20opposition%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20panel%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20now%20defunct%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20an%20opaque%20method%20of%20collecting%20donations%20by%20political%20parties%2C%20that%20has%20led%20to%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20cornering%20almost%2050%25%20of%20the%20total%20donations%20between%202017%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20evidence%20of%20arm-twisting%20too%2C%20reports%20claiming%2030%20companies%20donated%20%2440%20million%20to%20BJP%20after%20they%20faced%20criminal%20investigations%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20panel%20said%20that%20it%20was%20worried%20about%20the%20persistent%20refusal%20of%20the%20ECI%20to%20address%20possible%20flaws%20with%20the%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVM)%20and%20demands%20to%20ensure%20100%25%20Voter%20Verified%20Paper%20and%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20during%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20said%20that%20the%20ECI%20does%20not%20%E2%80%9Cprovide%20guarantees%20against%20hacking%2C%20tampering%2C%20and%20spurious%20vote%20injections%E2%80%9D%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20situation%20where%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20system%20was%20seen%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20robust%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20flagged%20its%20concerns%20about%20the%20increasing%20propensity%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmonopolise%E2%80%9D%20the%20information%20space%2C%20exclude%20opposition%20political%20parties%2C%C2%A0%20and%20control%20Indian%20media%20and%20its%20advertisement-driven%20revenue%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPro-BJP%20actors%20also%20dominate%20social%20media.%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20Cell%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20deliberately%20stoking%20communal%20hatred%20and%20spreading%20disinformation%2C%20under%20protection%20provided%20by%20its%20top%20leadership.%20BJP-led%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20have%20also%20intensified%20their%20muzzling%20of%20independent%20media%20and%20fact-checkers%2C%20including%20through%20the%20misuse%20of%20anti-terror%20and%20national%20security%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20and%20allied%20groups%20seem%20to%20have%20doubled%20down%20on%20religious%20polarisation%20for%20electoral%20gains%20%E2%80%93%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20presiding%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%202024%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20announcing%20rules%20to%20the%20discriminatory%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%202019%2C%20being%20cases%20in%20point.%20Direct%20calls%20to%20violence%20against%20Muslims%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%20continue%2C%20alongside%20dehumanising%20rhetoric%2C%20by%20influential%20leaders%2C%20in%20online%20as%20well%20as%20physical%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20noted%20the%20%E2%80%9Cemerging%20threats%20posed%20by%20AI-%20powered%20deepfake%20and%20other%20technology%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20the%20failure%20of%20ECI%20to%20strictly%20enforce%20%E2%80%9Cexisting%20laws%2C%20rules%20and%20model%20code%20for%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20ECI%20appears%20to%20have%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpro-government%20bias%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20way%20it%20decided%20the%20elections%20dates.%20The%20panel%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20election%20commissioners%20is%20now%20being%20done%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20empowering%20itself%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvirtual%20veto%E2%80%9D%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20then%20called%20upon%20the%20ECI%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20attentive%20to%20complaints%20where%20they%20concern%20citizens%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20universal%20suffrage%2C%20and%20on%20violations%20of%20MCC%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710658466000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16163914%2F2048px-BMC_Election_2012_-_Ink_mark_after_voting_6886404209.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpanel-of-five-scholars-will-be-monitoring-indias-2024-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20group%20plans%20to%20point%20out%20possible%20violations%20in%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20and%20whether%20there%20is%20an%20erosion%20of%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20political%20parties%20and%20voters%20from%20different%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpanel-of-five-scholars-will-be-monitoring-indias-2024-elections%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22