20unaccounted%20form%20is%20something%20that%20the%20entire%20nation%20has%20to%20work%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20the%20donor%E2%80%99s%20privacy%20is%20also%20protected%2C%20he%20is%20not%20harassed%2C%20how%20it%20is%20channelised%2C%20how%20it%20is%20more%20and%20more%20white.%20In%20the%20digital%20age%2C%20there%20must%20be%20a%20very%2C%20very%20less%20cash%20economy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20flip-flopping%20views%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20scheme%20and%20the%20court%20case%20against%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commission-has-no-comments-on-landmark-verdict-on-electoral-bonds-how-it-changed-its-stance%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20documented%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Goel%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20Kumar%20said%20the%20matter%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CMr%20Arun%20was%20a%20very%2C%20very%20distinguished%20member%20of%20our%20team%20and%20I%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20working%20with%20him%20all%20the%20time.%20But%20in%20every%20institution%20somebody%20will%20have%20to%20be%20given%20the%20personal%20space%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20personal%20space%20should%20not%20be%20touched%20and%20it%20is%20insensitive%20to%20ask%20personal%20questions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20remarks%20were%20made%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20to%20announce%20dates%20for%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20where%20Kumar%20was%20alongside%20the%20two%20new%20election%20commissioners%20appointed%20last%20week%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwho-are-the-new-election-commissioner-appointees-sukhbir-singh-sandhu-and-gyanesh-kumar%5C%22%3ESukhbir%20Singh%20Sandhu%20and%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710657478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F16200455%2F24ffc5eb-3f57-4e78-babc-397f2