hat%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20is%20blind%20faith%2C%20not%20hope.%20Indeed%20much%20of%20what%20gets%20called%20hope%20today%20actually%20includes%20beliefs%20held%20%3Cem%3Econtrary%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20evidence.%20These%20are%20fantasies%20or%20delusions%2C%20wishful%20thinking%20or%20wilful%20ignorance.%20All%20such%20false%20hopes%20are%20dangerous.%20They%20lull%20us%20into%20inaction.%20They%20guide%20us%20down%20wrong%20paths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20real%20hope%20is%20essential%20for%20human%20thriving.%20And%20real%20hope%20is%20built%20upon%20the%20possible.%20It%E2%80%99s%20arrived%20at%20by%20facing%20hard%20truths%2C%20understanding%20what%20the%20challenges%20truly%20are%2C%20and%20contemplating%20the%20difficult%20tradeoffs.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20passive%3B%20it%20arises%20through%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20363px)%2085vw%2C%20363px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22363%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896.jpg%20874w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-219x300.jpg%20219w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F11123728%2FIMG_2896-746x1024.jpg%20746w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696598%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22498%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%E2%80%99ve%20shown%20in%20this%20series%2C%20to%20significantly%20slow%20the%20rate%20of%20anthropogenic%20climate%20change%20and%20its%20underlying%20cause%20of%20ecological%20overshoot%20requires%20us%20to%20%3Cem%3Eradically%3C%2Fem%3E%20staunch%20emissions%20from%20combustible%20fossils%20%3Cem%3Ewhile%20also%3C%2Fem%3E%20broadly%20promoting%20global%20ecological%20integrity%2C%20including%20rebuilding%20fluidly%20equitable%20human%20societies%20%3Cem%3Ewithin%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20dynamic%20web%20of%20life.%20This%20unavoidably%20entails%20commensurately%20radical%20and%20rapid%20changes%20to%20our%20global%20economy%20and%20sociopolitical%20systems.%20But%20whether%20and%20how%20these%20might%20occur%20or%20be%20achieved%20remain%20open%20questions.%20Nor%20are%20the%20answers%20limited%20to%20matters%20of%20global%20cooperation%20through%20officialdom.%20Revolutionary%20reforms%20centred%20on%20our%20relationships%20with%20the%20Earth%20and%20each%20other%20will%20not%20be%20technocratically%20mandated%20from%20the%20top%20down.%20Given%20all%20this%2C%20it%20seems%20clear%20that%20hope%20must%20find%20purchase%20not%20in%20fantasies%20of%20continuing%20the%20present%20patterns%20of%20civilisation%2C%20but%20in%20departures%20from%20the%20world%20we%E2%80%99ve%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20I%20posit%20no%20faith%20in%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fthe-idea-of-green-growth-is-flawed-we-must-find-ways-of-using-and-wasting-less-energy-160432%5C%22%3EGreen%20Growth%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20mechanism%20for%20salvation%2C%20in%20which%20the%20world%20continues%20on%20as%20it%20is%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20using%20oil%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20coal%20we%20use%20%E2%80%98renewable%20energy%E2%80%99%20to%20continue%20over-extracting%20and%20over-polluting%20for%20continuous%20growth%20in%20consumption.%20I%20do%20not%20have%20faith%20that%20energy-sucking%20technological%20fixes%20or%20capitalist%20imperatives%20can%20fundamentally%20change%20our%20current%20trajectory%E2%80%94for%20these%20are%20the%20very%20engines%20of%20the%20same%20catastrophe%20we%20now%20would%20ask%20them%20to%20set%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20no%20faith%20that%20Western-styled%2C%20exclusionary%20models%20of%20%E2%80%98nature%20conservation%2C%E2%80%99%20which%20aren%E2%80%99t%20grounded%20in%20any%20genuine%20understanding%20of%20human%20interactions%20with%20the%20non-human%20world%2C%20will%20help%20to%20restore%20balance%20or%20mutualism%20between%20people%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20life.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20faith%20that%20the%20present%20configuration%20of%20neocolonial%20geopolitics%20will%20promote%20social%20equity%20contributing%20to%20environmental%20sustainability.%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20encourage%20wealth%20ceilings%20and%20austerity%20for%20the%20wealthy%20in%20order%20to%20end%20the%20present%20regimes%20of%20oppression%2C%20violence%2C%20and%20dispossession%20meted%20out%20against%20Indigenous%20peoples%2C%20disenfranchised%20social%20castes%20and%20classes%20and%20ethnicities%20or%20women%2C%20whose%20energies%20and%20resources%20are%20presently%20co-opted%20to%20enable%20elite%20over-consumption%20and%20power.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20faith%20that%20any%20business-as-usual%20state%20of%20affairs%E2%80%94%E2%80%98green%E2%80%99%20or%20otherwise%E2%80%94can%20address%20our%20ecological%20overshoot.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20faith%20that%20our%20extractive%20industrial%20system%20can%20continue%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-human-animal-in-the-circle-of-life%5C%22%3Eplundering%20the%20Earth%3C%2Fa%3E%20much%20longer%20before%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20faith%20in%20precisely%20such%20delusions%20is%20what%20gets%20promulgated%20as%20hope%20by%20most%20leading%20voices%20in%20the%20global%20conversations%20on%20climate%20change.%20Most%20of%20these%20are%20ensconced%20in%20the%20Global%20North%20or%20the%20upper-tiers%20of%20international%20wealth%2C%20deeply%20invested%20in%20maintaining%20the%20sociopolitical%20and%20economic%20structures%20of%20the%20present%20world.%20Most%20of%20these%20folks%20understandably%20fear%20actions%20that%20would%20fundamentally%20change%20this%20system.%20Thus%2C%20they%20generally%20avoid%20questions%20that%20expose%20the%20folly%20of%20our%