%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fbooks%2Findia-approach-global-warming%5C%22%3EIndian%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20commitment%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20fighting%20climate%20change%20includes%20building%20more%20solar%20farms%20and%20hydropower%20dams%E2%80%94megaprojects%20that%20lead%20to%20ecosystem%20destruction%2C%20loss%20of%20species%2C%20and%20the%20mass%20displacement%20of%20Adivasis%20and%20others%20already%20living%20low-consumption%20lifestyles%2C%20in%20order%20to%20promote%20higher%20consumption%20among%20a%20wealthier%20set.%20India%20also%20intends%20to%20build%20more%20coal%20power%20plants%2C%20which%20emit%20massive%20greenhouse%20gasses%20and%20noxious%20particulates.%20The%20purpose%20of%20this%20destruction%20is%20to%20meet%20the%20rising%20demand%20for%20energy%20that%20industrial%20consumerist%20lifestyles%20require%E2%80%94our%20common%20aspirations%20of%20socioeconomic%20rise%20and%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%20being%20effectively%20the%20same%20as%20an%20aspiration%20to%20increase%20our%20energy%20and%20materials%20consumption%E2%80%94%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Four-insatiable-quest-for-fire%5C%22%3Eincluding%20fossil%20fuels%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20fight%20climate%20change%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20whole%20system%E2%80%94the%20social%2C%20cultural%2C%20technological%20edifice%20of%20modern%20society%E2%80%94that%20will%20need%20to%20change%3B%20whereas%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20official%20responses%20are%20largely%20targeted%20at%20shifting%20our%20place%20within%20the%20existing%20system.%20The%20present%20blueprint%20to%20create%20more%20energy%20is%20no%20path%20toward%20sustainability%3A%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20promote%20the%20recovery%20of%20the%20biosphere.%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20forestall%20the%20heating%20of%20the%20planet.%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20dismantle%20the%20economically%20centralising%20forces%20of%20the%20present%20economy%20that%20steal%20from%20the%20disenfranchised%20peripheries%20to%