the%20fossil%20energy%20used%20today%20around%20the%20world%E2%80%94let%20alone%20to%20continuously%20%3Cem%3Eincrease%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20in%20support%20of%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20plans%20for%20%E2%80%98Green%20Growth%E2%80%99%20seem%20to%20presume%20an%20ability%20to%20continue%20providing%20energy%20and%20materials%20in%20the%20same%20fashion%20as%20today.%20There%E2%80%99s%20not%20even%20apparently%20any%20accounting%20for%20such%20considerations%20as%2C%20for%20example%2C%20that%20making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldcoal.org%2Fcoal-facts%2Fcoal-steel%2F%5C%22%3Esteel%20depends%20upon%20coal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20only%20as%20a%20heating%20fuel%2C%20but%20as%20a%20reagent%20in%20the%20ore-refining%20process.%20Or%20that%20industrial%20processes%20are%20fundamentally%20dependent%20upon%20petrochemicals.%20That%20most%20modern%20goods%E2%80%94including%20electric%20cars!%E2%80%94are%20substantially%20made%20of%20oil-derived%20plastics%20and%20coatings.%20Or%20that%20the%20manufacture%20and%20movement%20of%20raw%20materials%20and%20goods%20can%20never%20be%20as%20cheap%20and%20easy%20as%20they%20are%20today%2C%20when%20they%E2%80%99re%20underwritten%20by%20the%20unique%20properties%20of%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20hopelessness%20of%20techno-optimist%20%E2%80%98solutions%E2%80%99%20is%20that%20they%20take%20into%20account%20neither%20the%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20biophysical%20limits%20nor%20the%20injustice%20of%20the%20resource-grabs%20or%20environmental%20damage%20they%20entail.%20They%20wholly%20miss%20the%20ground%20reality%20of%20our%20predicament%3A%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20mired%20in%20ecological%20overshoot%20built%20upon%20deep%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-agricultural-revolution-an-alternate-telling%5C%22%3Emultilayered%20histories%20of%20environmental%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20social%20over-exploitation.%20Yet%20the%20arbiters%20of%20the%20global%20conversation%20on%20climate