ompare%20the%20media%20outrage%20over%20that%20corruption-ridden%20gun%20deal%20and%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20scam%20that%20is%20roiling%20the%20country%20today.%20The%20first%2C%20which%20yielded%20bribes%20amounting%20to%20Rs%2064%20crore%2C%20led%20to%20the%20Opposition%20resigning%20en%20masse%20and%20the%20defeat%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20in%20the%20general%20election%20of%201989%3B%20the%20other%20%E2%80%93%20which%20like%20the%20first%20directly%20involved%20the%20ruling%20establishment%20%E2%80%94%20was%20marked%20by%20the%20conspicuously%20pusillanimous%20stance%20of%20news%20television%20and%20newspapers%2C%20despite%20strong%20evidence%20that%20the%20bonds%20were%20really%20a%20sordid%20cover-up%20for%20bribery%2C%20blackmailing%20and%20backslapping%20at%20the%20highest%20political%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20story%20points%20to%20how%20effective%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20in%20dismantling%20much%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20mainstream%20media%20through%20a%20strategy%20of%20fear%20peddling%2C%20personal%20patronage%20and%20the%20systematic%20courting%20and%20control%20of%20proprietors.%20It%20also%20points%20to%20the%20emergence%20of%20what%20is%20often%20termed%20the%20%E2%80%9Calternative%20media%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20online%20news%20portals%2C%20YouTube%20channels%2C%20even%20single%20journalist-driven%20outlets%20%E2%80%94%20which%20far%20outstripped%20the%20mainstream%20media%20in%20the%20coverage%20of%20this%20story.%20Not%20having%20lost%20their%20appetite%20for%20credible%2C%20establishment-exposing%20news%2C%20they%20emerged%20as%20the%20true%20Fourth%20Estate%20in%20the%20country.%20Little%20wonder%20then%20that%20it%20is%20this%20category%20of%20the%20media%20which%20has%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20the%20latest%20raft%20of%20media-gagging%20efforts%20mounted%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20through%20various%20orders%20issued%20under%20Information%20Technology%20(Intermediary%20Guidelines%20and%20Digital%20Ethics%20Code)%20Rules%2C%202021.%20The%20strike%20launched%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20last%20October%20is%20indicative%20of%20the%20very%20deep%20anxieties%20that%20the%20political%20establishment%20harbours%20of%20minuscule%20players%20with%20minds%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20Electoral%20Bonds%20became%20a%20part%20of%20the%20political%20landscape%2C%20there%20have%20been%20some%20remarkable%20efforts%20put%20in%20by%20alternative%20media%20to%20expose%20their%20perfidy%2C%20often%20drawing%20upon%20information%20unearthed%20by%20transparency%20bodies%20like%20the%20ADR%20and%20indefatigable%20RTI%20crusaders%20like%20Commodore%20Lokesh%20Batra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202019%2C%20the%20now%20defunct%20%3Cem%3EHuffPost%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20made%20full%20use%20of%20information%20unearthed%20through%20RTI%20applications%20to%20reveal%20how%20instructions%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20ensured%20that%20Rs%2010%20crore%20worth%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20redeemed%20despite%20having%20expired.%20This%20was%20just%20before%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%20of%202018%20and%20the%20very%20fact%20that%20the%20PMO%20took%20such%20a%20close%20interest%20in%20this%20matters%20points%20to%20which%20party%20was%20the%20principal%20beneficiary%20of%20those%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20Poonam%20Agarwal%2C%20formerly%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Quint%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20who%20now%20has%20her%20own%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20%3Cem%3EexplainX%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20emerged%20in%20its%20paper%20avatar%20in%202018%2C%20she%20did%20an%20investigative%20report%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Quint%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20buying%20them.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%E2%80%98%E2%80%99Unique%20Numbers%20Recorded%20by%20SBI%E2%80%99%3A%20Investigative%20Journalist%20Who%20Bought%20Electoral%20Bond%E2%80%99)%2C%20Agarwal%20looks%20back%20at%20that%20important%20purchase%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20my%20%3Cem%3Ecuriosity%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20made%20me%20get%20a%20forensic%20test%20done%20of%20the%20bond.%20When%20I%20gave%20my%20Rs%201%2C000%20bond%20to%20the%20Truth%20lab%20forensic%20lab%20to%20test%2C%20they%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20hidden%20unique%20number%20which%20is%20visible%20under%20UV%20Ray.%20To%20prove%20that%20it%20is%20a%20unique%20number%2C%20I%20purchased%20one%20more%20bond%20worth%20Rs%201%2C000%20and%20got%20its%20forensic%20test%20done.%20Both%20the%20bonds%20had%20different%20numbers%20hidden%20in%20the%20bonds.%20Hence%20it%20was%20proven%20that%20bonds%20carry%20hidden%20unique%20numbers.%E2%80%9D%20This%20alphanumeric%20code%2C%20visible%20only%20under%20ultraviolet%20rays%2C%20is%20today%20very%20much%20in%20the%20news%20since%20it%20links%20the%20donor%20and%20their%20party%20of%20choice.%20Curiosity%2C%20which%20in%20this%20case%20drove%20the%20investigation%2C%20is%20the%20stuff%20of%20great%20journalism%20but%20it%20has%20to%20be%20given%20free%20rein%20in%20a%20newsroom%20that%20does%20not%20pull%20its%20punches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F08223208%2Frupee-g9dbf1131e_1280-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-627652%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20Indian%20currency%20notes.%20Photo%3A%20rupixen.com%2FPixabay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Reporters%E2%80%99%20Collective%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EArticle%2014%20%3C%2Fem%3Eput%20out%20details%20on%20what%20lies%20in%20those%20sealed%20covers.%20%E2%80%98Electoral%20Bonds%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20sealed%20cover%20on%20Electoral%20Bonds.%20Opened.%20So%20Easily%E2%80%99%20(%3Cem%3ETRC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20June%206%2C%202022)%20and%20%E2%80%98Debunking%20a%20%E2%80%98Sealed%E2%80%99%20Myth%E2%80%99%20(%3Cem%3EA14%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20June%206%2C%202022)%20pointed%20to%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20hear%20the%20case%20in%202019.%20These%20two%20digital%20media%20organisations%20then%20went%20on%20to%20reveal%20what%20lay%20in%20those%20sealed%20envelopes%20presented%20to%20the%20apex%20court.%20They%20did%20this%20through%20the%20simple%20expedient%20of%20interviewing%20party%20leaders%20and%20crunching%20data%20from%20annual%20audit%20report%20filings%20of%20political%20parties.%20They%20thus%20discovered%2C%20two%20years%20before%20the%20present%20revelations%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9C105%20political%20parties%20did%20not%20receive%20funds%20from%20Electoral%20Bonds.%20Only%2019%20political%20parties%20did.%20Between%202017-18%20and%202019-20%2C%20they%20received%20Rs%206%2C201%20crore.%C2%A0And%20a%20whopping%20sixty-eight%20percent%20of%20this%20unaccounted%20money%20was%20cornered%20by%20one%20party%2C%C2%A0the%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20kept%20a%20keen%20eye%20on%20the%20ball%20from%20the%20early%20days.%20On%20May%202018%2C%20it%20carried%20a%20story%20%2C%20%E2%80%98Centre%20Overlooked%20EC%E2%80%99s%20Concerns%20on%20Changes%20to%20Laws%20on%20Political%20Funding%E2%80%99%20based%20on%20the%20RTI%20application%20of%20Pune%20resident%20Vihar%20Durve%2C%20which%20unearthed%20the%20letter%20the%20EC%20had%20sent%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Law%20and%20Justice.%20It%20had%20termed%20the%20step%20to%20institute%20Electoral%20Bonds%20as%20a%20retrograde%20one%20and%20also%20expressed%20the%20fear%20that%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20shell%20companies%20for%20purposes%20of%20political%20donations.%20It%20is%20another%20matter%20that%20this%20wise%20and%20timely%20warning%20was%20completely%20ignored%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%C2%A0%20In%20January%202020%20came%20another%20%3Cem%3EWire%20%3C%2Fem%3Estory%20uncovered%20the%20shoddy%20origins%20of%20this%20scheme%20(%E2%80%98RTI%20Reveals%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%20Passed%20After%20Only%20%E2%80%98Informal%20Discussion%E2%80%99%20Among%20Officials%E2%80%99).%20It%20cited%20a%20file%20noting%20which%20revealed%20that%20a%20briefing%20meet%20was%20hosted%20%E2%80%9Cby%20the%20Minister%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20on%20March%208%2C%202017%20where%20the%20proposal%20for%20issuing%20electoral%20bonds%20following%20amendment%20to%20the%20RBI%20Act%2C%201934%2C%20was%20raised.%20It%20was%20stated%20that%20this%20%E2%80%98will%20bring%20much%20awaited%20reform%20for%20giving%2Freceiving%20of%20donations%20for%2F%20by%20political%20parties.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStriking%20too%20is%20that%20even%20as%20the%20Electoral%20Bonds%20story%20was%20breaking%20in%20late%20February%20this%20year%2C%20two%20online%20portals%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ENewslaundry%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Newsminute%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20were%20the%20first%20to%20interpret%20the%20initial%20data%20on%20the%20money%20trail%20(%E2%80%98Part%201%3A%20Behind%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rise%20and%20rise%2C%20bonds%2C%20trusts%20and%20raids%20on%20corporates%E2%80%99%2C%20February%2020).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20just%20a%20few%20instances%20of%20internet%20media%20organisation%20that%20did%20not%20forget%20their%20journalism.%20There%20are%20many%20others%20who%20worked%20equally%20hard%20on%20exposing%20one%20of%20our%20biggest%20scams%20in%20recent%20history.%20Today%2C%20as%20we%20rue%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20Indians%20were%20sold%20a%20lemon%20through%20these%20bonds%3B%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20ruling%20party%20was%20able%20to%20strike%20gold%20and%20use%20it%20to%20destroy%20electoral%20democracy%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Indian%20public%20needs%20to%20acknowledge%20and%20support%20the%20invaluable%20work%20of%20these%20modest%20online%20media%20establishments%20which%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20moral%20conscience%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20the%20toxic%20newsroom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20senior%20Mumbai-based%20Satish%20Nandgoankar%2C%20a%20senior%20editor%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20has%20led%20to%20a%20rare%20moment%20of%20introspection%20and%20exposure%20within%20the%20media%20community.%20The%20Mumbai%20Press%20Club%20conducted%20its%20own%20inquiry%20into%20the%20circumstances%20of%20Nandgoankar%E2%80%99s%20death%20by%20interviewing%20those%20who%20knew%20him%20and%20inviting%20his%20wife%20to%20speak%20to%20its%20members.%20Many%20unsavoury%20details%20emerged%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20Nandgaonkar%20had%20been%20intensely%20humiliated%20by%20his%20editor%20over%20a%20delayed%20story%2C%20and%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cuseless%E2%80%9D.%20The%20inquiry%20also%20revealed%20that%20Nandgoankar%20had%20tried%20to%20help%20freelancers%20whose%20stories%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20to%20the%20print%20edition%2C%20by%20uploading%20their%20stories%20online.%20%C2%A0A%20few%20days%20before%20his%20death%2C%20the%20responsibility%20for%20uploading%20stories%20was%20taken%20away%20from%20him.%20All%20these%20developments%20and%20feelings%20of%20humiliation%20could%20have%20triggered%20the%20heart%20attack%20that%20took%20his%20life.%20On%20March%201%2C%20Mumbai%20Press%20Club%20sent%20out%20an%20open%20letter%20to%20editors%2C%20media%20houses%2C%20and%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%2C%20appealing%20for%20newsrooms%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Csafe%20and%20supportive%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20has%20become%20difficult%20to%20find%20in%20these%20times%20of%20an%20intensely%20competitive%20work%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20pointed%20out%20how%20toxicity%20percolates%20from%20the%20top%20editorial%20leadership%20who%20often%20enjoy%20the%20support%20of%20the%20management.%20This%20makes%20it%20incumbent%2C%20it%20said%2C%20for%20bodies%20like%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%20to%20intervene%20and%20investigate%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20these%20developments%2C%20the%20online%20portal%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Citizen%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20carried%20a%20three-part%20series%20on%20newsroom%20dominated%20by%20bullies%20(%E2%80%98Journalism%20At%20Work%20%E2%80%93%20Toxic%20Newsrooms%E2%80%99%2C%20March%2014).%20It%20quoted%20one%20employer%20who%20observed%20that%20the%20organisation%20she%20worked%20in%20%E2%80%9Cfunctioned%20like%20a%20family-run%20local%20grocery%20shop.%20Irrespective%20of%20their%20education%2C%20the%20owners%20had%20no%20respect%20or%20decency%20to%20speak%20with%20the%20employees.%20The%20language%20they%20used%20was%20extremely%20derogatory.%E2%80%9D%20Her%20editor%2C%20she%20added%2C%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Chorrible%20person%20and%20she%20would%20go%20to%20any%20extreme%20to%20demean%20the%20employees%20by%20howling%20at%20them%20in%20front%20of%20the%20entire%20office%20or%20in%20the%20WhatsApp%20groups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20the%20first%20month%20of%20her%20joining%20work%20she%20had%20her%20first%20panic%20attack%2C%20after%20being%20humiliated%20in%20an%20office%20Whatsapp%20group%20of%20more%20than%20100%20employees.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20second%20time%20I%20had%20a%20panic%20attack%20in%20the%20office%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20have%20a%20stroke%2Fheart%20attack.%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20going%20to%20die%20right%20there%20on%20the%20spot.%20The%20working%20hours%2C%20condition%2C%20ambience%2C%20work%20culture%2C%20the%20bosses%2C%20the%20meetings%2C%20the%20schedules%2C%20the%20salary%E2%80%A6%20every%20basic%20thing%20there%20was%20inhuman.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENandgoankar%E2%80%99s%20death%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20an%20industry%20that%20is%20sleep%20walking%20into%20a%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERelease%20NewsClick%E2%80%99s%20founder-editor%20now!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpts%20from%20the%20statement%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Union%20of%20Journalists%2C%20which%20is%20organising%20a%20protest%20meeting%20today%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSixteen%20journalists%2C%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20are%20currently%20charged%20under%20the%20draconian%20UAPA.%20Seven%20among%20them%20are%20in%20jails%20or%20under%20arrest.%C2%A0%20Eight%20journalists%20are%20on%20bail%20with%20UAPA%20charges%20on%20them.%20One%20journalist%20is%20charged%20but%20not%20arrested%20and%20one%20has%20been%20acquitted%20of%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20October%203%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20arrested%20eminent%20editor%20and%20columnist%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20used%20foreign%20funds%20to%20report%20on%20protests%20by%20farmers%20and%20workers%2C%20the%20struggles%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20and%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20movements.%20The%20police%20and%20the%20authorities%20have%20opposed%20the%20bail%20applications%20of%2074-year-old%20Purkayastha%2C%20despite%20his%20advanced%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJournalists%20in%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20small%2C%20independent%20media%20organisation%20founded%20by%20Mr.%20Purkayastha%2C%20were%20raided%20and%20interrogated%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20other%20agencies.%20About%20400%20mobile%20phones%20and%20laptops%20were%20seized%20from%20the%20homes%20of%20these%20journalists.%20The%20Police%20have%20not%20returned%20these%20despite%20multiple%20complaints%20and%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20has%20made%20huge%20demands%20that%20amount%20to%20freezing%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Consequently%2C%20about%20100%20journalists%20and%20other%20employees%20associated%20with%20the%20organisation%20have%20not%20received%20their%20salaries%20for%20the%20last%20three%20months.%20The%20organisation%20has%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%20Income%20Tax%20decision%20in%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20seizure%20of%20electronic%20equipment%20and%20the%20denial%20of%20access%20to%20salaries%20is%20a%20direct%20and%20blatant%20attack%20on%20the%20right%20to%20livelihood.%20It%20poses%20severe%20hurdles%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20journalists%E2%80%99%20professional%20duties.%20All%20these%20point%20towards%20a%20strategy%20of%20this%20government%20to%20muzzle%20independent%20media%20which%20voices%20the%20issues%20of%20workers%20and%20farmers.%20During%20the%20ongoing%20protests%20of%20farmers%2C%20even%20X%2F%20twitter%20accounts%20and%20other%20social%20media%20handles%20of%20several%20journalists%20and%20independent%20media%20houses%20have%20been%20blocked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20amplify%20Israeli%20official-speak%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVenkatesh%20takes%20issue%20with%20the%20piece%20entitled%2C%20%E2%80%98Hezbollah%20Rocket%20Attack%3A%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20Asks%20Citizens%20to%20Leave%20Border%20Areas%E2%80%99%20(March%205)%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20article%20could%20have%20done%20with%20better%20nuance%20and%20better%20information.%C2%A0%20For%20starters%2C%20why%20amplify%20Israeli%20official-speak%20such%20as%20calling%20Hezbollah%20a%20%E2%80%9CShia%20terror%20organisation%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20Most%20clear-thinking%20people%20know%20and%20vocalise%20it%20as%20a%20resistance%20operation%20legitimately%20involved%20in%20ejecting%20occupiers%20from%20their%20land.%20Hezbollah%20officials%20are%20part%20of%20the%20Lebanese%20parliament%3B%20UN%20policies%20support%20occupation%20resistance!%20Which%20brings%20me%20to%20the%20next%20point%3A%20the%20spot%20where%20Pat%20was%20killed%20is%20euphemistically%20termed%20%E2%80%9CMargaliot%2C%20a%20northern%20border%20community%20in%20Israel.%E2%80%9D%20This%20region%20is%20itself%20part%20of%20the%20spoils%20of%20the%201948%20Nakba.%20Ten%20minutes%20of%20research%20would%20have%20established%20this.%20The%20article%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20October%208%2C%20Hezbollah%20has%20intensified%20rocket%20launch%20attacks%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20northern%20communities%20and%20military%20installations%2C%20purportedly%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%20Surely%20you%20know%20that%20Israel%20has%20been%20bombing%20Lebanon%2C%20Syria%20and%20Gaza%20and%20that%20Hezbollah%20is%20likely%20responding%20to%20Israeli%20provocation%20and%20not%20necessarily%20%E2%80%9Cpurportedly%E2%80%9D%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Wire%20must%20up%20its%20game!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalling%20on%20Bhutan%20to%20free%20political%20prisoners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMail%20from%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EDr%20Roshmi%20Goswami%2C%20co-chairperson%20and%20Dr%20P.%20Saravanamuttu%2C%20bureau%20member%2C%20of%20South%20Asians%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(SAHR)%2C%20a%20regional%20network%20of%20human%20rights%20defenders%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CSAHR%20has%20called%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20Bhutan%20to%20release%20the%20political%20prisoners%20it%20has%20detained%20for%20decades.%20It%20made%20the%20call%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%2016th%20World%20Social%20Forum%20(WSF)%20held%20in%20Nepal%2C%20where%20a%20session%20was%20organised%20on%20%E2%80%98Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20Prisoners%20of%20Conscience%E2%80%99.%20The%20session%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Bhutanese%20citizens%20of%20Nepali%20origin%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Lhotshampas%2C%20which%20started%20in%20the%20late%201980%E2%80%99s%20into%20the%20early%201990%E2%80%99s.%C2%A0While%20the%20situation%20of%20the%20Lhotshampa%20refugees%20was%20relatively%20well%20known%2C%20the%20reality%20of%20political%20prisoners%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20have%20spent%20more%20than%2030%20years%20in%20Chamjang%20Jail%2C%20has%20only%20recently%20been%20reported.%20Further%2C%20there%20are%20also%20significant%20numbers%20of%20disappeared%20citizens%20of%20Bhutan%20about%20whom%20not%20much%20is%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20at%20present%20Bhutan%20puts%20up%20a%20front%20of%20a%20country%20high%20on%20the%20Gross%20National%20Happiness%20index%2C%20it%20hides%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20Lhotshampas%20who%20were%20strategically%20expelled%2C%20made%20stateless%2C%20and%20also%20detained%20as%20prisoners%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98non-nationals%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98anti-nationals%E2%80%99.%20These%20Prisoners%20of%20Conscience%20are%20held%20in%20prison%20for%20their%20expressions%20of%20political%20beliefs%20or%20identity%20assertion%2C%20while%20others%20have%20been%20framed.%20Different%20international%20human%20rights%20organisations%20have%20recognised%2050-100%20people%20are%20still%20held%20as%20political%20prisoners%20in%20Bhutan%2C%20without%20trials%20or%20cases%20being%20brought%2C%20with%2037%20kept%20in%20Chamgang%20Jail%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSAHR%20believes%20that%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20progression%20towards%20a%20democratic%20state%2C%20where%20the%20citizenry%20is%20truly%20%E2%80%98happy%E2%80%99%20and%20content%2C%20requires%20the%20release%20of%20the%20prisoners%20of%20conscience.%20SAHR%20further%20calls%20on%20the%20international%20community%2C%20including%20Nepal%20as%20the%20host%20country%20of%20refugees%20and%20India%20as%20a%20country%20that%20has%20not%20done%20its%20bit%20on%20the%20refugee%20issue%20being%20the%20land%20neighbour%20of%20Bhutan%20and%20with%20deep%20links%20to%20the%20Bhutanese%20state%2C%20to%20work%20to%20persuade%20Bhutan%20to%20take%20back%20the%20refugees%20who%20have%20refused%20to%20take%20the%20option%20of%20third-country%20settlement.%20These%20Lhotshampa%20refugees%20languish%20in%20the%20camps%20of%20Southeast%20Nepal%2C%20maintaining%20a%20principled%20stand%20on%20their%20%E2%80%98right%20of%20return%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSAHR%20is%20also%20concerned%20that%20the%20remaining%20several%20thousand%20refugees%20in%20southeast%20Nepal%20are%20now%20without%20support%20of%20international%20organisations%20such%20as%20UNHCR%20and%20WFP.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Nepal%20has%20disbanded%20the%20refugee%20camps%2C%20and%20it%20has%20also%20become%20difficult%20for%20the%20refugees%20to%20move%20about%20and%20lead%20normal%20lives.%20SAHR%20demands%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20Nepal%20as%20well%20as%20international%20organisations%20re-engage%20with%20Bhutanese%20refugees%20and%20provide%20support%20and%20security%20to%20the%20refugees%20still%20in%20Nepal%E2%80%A6The%20Lhotshampa%20refugees%20in%20Nepal%20have%20the%20right%20to%20decent%20living%20and%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20for%20which%20they%20should%20have%20the%20right%20to%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWrite%20to%20%3Cem%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710599376000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F23203159%2FScreen-Shot-2020-10-23-at-8.31.43-PM.png%22%2C%22originID