%20sunny%20weather.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20couple%20moved%20back%20to%20Mission%20Viejo%20in%20December%202023%20and%20they%20never%20want%20to%20leave%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Wendy%20and%20Kurt%20Meyer%2C%20a%2065-year-old%20manufacturing%20manager%20and%2059-year-old%20toolmaker%2C%20who%20moved%20from%20Mission%20Viejo%2C%20California%2C%20to%20Washington%2C%20Iowa%2C%20in%20October%202021.%20They%20stayed%2020%20months%20before%20moving%20back%20to%20Mission%20Viejo%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I'm%20a%20native%20Californian%2C%20born%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%20My%20parents%20were%20from%20Iowa%20and%20moved%20me%20to%20Iowa%20when%20I%20was%20in%20high%20school.%20That's%20where%20I%20met%20my%20first%20husband%20and%20had%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20got%20divorced%2C%20I%20came%20back%20to%20California%20and%20met%20Kurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20Germany.%20In%202001%2C%20I%20was%20sent%20to%20Long%20Beach%20for%20business%20by%20my%20company.%20That's%20how%20I%20met%20Wendy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe'll%20have%20been%20married%20for%2022%20years%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20planned%20on%20retiring%20and%20spending%2050%25%20of%20our%20time%20here%20in%20California%20and%20the%20other%2050%25%20in%20Germany.%20But%20Kurt%20just%20loved%20California%20so%20much%20that%20in%202019%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20home%20in%20Germany.%20The%20intent%20was%20to%20stay%20here%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lived%20in%20Mission%20Viejo%20in%20Orange%20County.%20Our%20lives%20were%20awesome.%20We%20had%20great%20jobs.%20My%20daughter%20and%20grandkids%20were%20here.%20We%20had%20a%20good%20friend%20group%20and%20a%20great%20church.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20was%20perfect.%20I%20do%20half-marathons%2C%20and%20I%20could%20train%20year-round%20at%20the%20beach.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20Kurt%20and%20I%20would%20go%20for%20a%20walk%20in%20the%20water.%20Everything%20was%20in%20place%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20only%20thing%20we%20didn't%20like%20was%20the%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20started%20contemplating%20a%20move%20in%202021%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMy%20daughter%20and%20her%20husband%20and%20two%20kids%20traveled%20to%20Iowa%20to%20visit%20family.%20When%20she%20came%20back%2C%20she%20announced%20they%20were%20moving%20there.%20She's%20a%20native%20Iowan%20and%20wanted%20a%20better%20lifestyle%20for%20her%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20son%20also%20ended%20up%20moving%20to%20Iowa.%20He%20retired%20from%20the%20Air%20Force%20and%20moved%20back%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20moving.%20None.%20We%20had%20even%20talked%20about%20how%20we%20would%20never%20live%20in%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20we%20saw%20their%20moving%20truck%20pull%20out.%20I%20could%20almost%20weep%2C%20even%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20week%2C%20I%20contacted%20a%20real-estate%20agent.%20In%20October%202021%2C%20we%20started%20preparing%20to%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20was%20nervous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20was%2C%20too.%20There%20are%20as%20many%20people%20in%20Orange%20County%20as%20there%20are%20in%20the%20entire%20state%20of%20Iowa!%20Only%20about%20three%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20cup%20is%20always%20half%20full.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20had%20started%20missing%20Iowa%2C%20where%20I%20raised%20my%20kids.%20I%20missed%20that%20lifestyle%2C%20with%20the%20farmers%20market%2C%20the%20four%20seasons%2C%20the%20simplicity%20of%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20we%20bought%20a%20home%20in%20Iowa.%20We%20got%20a%20utility%20trailer%20and%20hauled%20all%20of%20our%20stuff%20ourselves%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kurt%20and%20Wendy%20pose%20for%20separate%20photos%20in%20Iowa.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f4af513037f8e81750fddd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20said%20they%20appreciated%20the%20open%20space%20in%20Iowa%20and%20being%20closer%20to%20family.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Meyer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20town%20we%20picked%20was%20very%20small.%20It's%20called%20Washington%2C%20Iowa%2C%20about%20half%20an%20hour%20south%20of%20Iowa%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20told%20ourselves%20before%20we%20left%20that%20we%20would%20give%20it%20one%20year.%20After%20one%20year%2C%20Kurt%20and%20I%20would%20sit%20down%20and%20do%20a%20pros%20and%20cons%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20plan%20was%20to%20retire%20once%20we%20got%20to%20Iowa.%20That's%20what%20we%20told%20ourselves.%20And%20we%20tried.%20But%20we%20didn't%20really%20want%20to%20retire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20boring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20think%20we%20were%20both%20so%20involved%20in%20the%20leaving%20process%20and%20the%20starting%20over%20process%20that%20we%20never%20thought%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20once%20those%20processes%20were%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20discovered%20retirement%20was%20so%20boring%20that%20my%20husband%20went%20and%20got%20a%20job%20at%20The%20University%20of%20Iowa%20Hospital%20in%20the%20engineering%20department.%20It%20was%20the%20best%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20this%20beautiful%20ranch-style%20home%20on%20half%20an%20acre.%20We%20found%20a%20great%20church.%20I%20worked%20part-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20loved%20how%20much%20space%20there%20was%20in%20Iowa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere%20was%20plenty%20of%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20also%20felt%20extremely%20patriotic%20there.%20People%20wear%20their%20patriotism%20right%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20and%20I%20loved%20that.%20I%20loved%20seeing%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20have%20been%20perfect%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBut%20it%20just%20wasn't%20our%20cup%20of%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20knew%20Iowa%20wasn't%20right%20for%20us%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20my%20god%2C%20I%20love%20this!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20this%20perception%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20did%20too%20%E2%80%94%20that%20Iowa%20is%20way%20more%20affordable.%20It's%20not.%20There%20are%20certain%20things%20that%20are%20more%20affordable%2C%20like%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20utilities%20weren't%20more%20affordable%2C%20because%20Iowa%20has%20such%20extreme%20shifts%20in%20the%20weather.%20I%20was%20shocked%20at%20the%20extreme%20fluctuations%20in%20the%20weather.%20The%20seasons%20roll%20right%20into%20each%20other.%20I%20don't%20even%20remember%20Fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnd%20our%20property%20taxes%20were%20twice%20what%20they%20are%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGas%20is%20cheaper%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20drive%20further.%20We%20had%20to%20drive%2040%20minutes%20to%20get%20to%20a%20Costco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Mission%20Viejo%2C%20we%20had%20concerts%20we%20could%20go%20to%20every%20summer.%20They%20don't%20have%20that%20in%20Iowa.%20I%20like%20to%20speed%20walk%20and%20do%20races%20and%20there%20were%20hardly%20any%20races%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222325%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kurt%20Meyer%20shovels%20snow%20in%20Iowa.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f4ad5b857f90b71523233d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221483%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWendy%20and%20Kurt%20Meyer%20said%20they%20were%20surprised%20by%20he%20extreme%20fluctuations%20in%20Iowa's%20weather.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wendy%20Meyer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnd%20we%20had%20moved%20half%20an%20hour's%20drive%20from%20where%20Wendy's%20daughter%20and%20her%20family%20lived%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20see%20them%20very%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey're%20busy%20with%20their%20own%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20kept%20actually%20saying%20to%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20I%20like%20this%20more%3F%20What%20is%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20then%2C%20one%20day%2C%20I%20remember%20telling%20Kurt%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20you%20to%20feel%20stuck%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20felt%20very%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20I%20felt%20that%20same%20way%20until%20one%20day%2C%20I%20got%20a%20text%20from%20my%20boss%20at%20our%20old%20jobs%20in%20California%20who%20said%20coming%20back%20was%20always%20an%20option.%20It%20made%20me%20realize%20we%20seriously%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20get%20our%20jobs%20back.%20I%20couldn't%20turn%20my%20back%20on%20how%20I%20felt%20in%20that%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20swear%2C%20as%20fast%20as%20we%20said%20we%20were%20going%20to%20Iowa%2C%20we%20decided%20we%20were%20going%20home.%20In%20total%2C%20we%20were%20in%20Iowa%20for%2020%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalifornia%20just%20feels%20like%20home%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20came%20back%20to%20where%20we%20had%20previously%20lived%20in%20Mission%20Viejo%2C%20literally%20within%20two%20miles%20of%20our%20old%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20just%20crazy%20how%20we%20were%20able%20to%20pick%20right%20back%20up.%20I%20started%20a%20part-time%20job%20this%20week.%20We've%20been%20very%20blessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20miss%20the%20kids.%20But%20we%20Zoom%20with%20them.%20And%20they%20come%20to%20visit.%20I%20go%20there%20too%20and%20hang%20out%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20young%20at%20heart.%20We%20weren't%20ready%20to%20retire.%20We're%20very%20active%20%E2%80%94%20way%20more%20active%20compared%20to%20others.%20We%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20life%20left%20in%20us%2C%20and%20we%20really%20appreciate%20everything%20California%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKurt's%20favorite%20saying%20is%3A%20Every%20day%20is%20paradise.%20We%20never%20vacation%20because%20why%20would%20we%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20see%20California%20with%20new%20eyes%20after%20this%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWendy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20see%20ourselves%20staying%20here%20in%20California%20for%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKurt%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EUntil%20the%20bitter%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-california-iowa-retire-stayed-less-than-2-years-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710591061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f4ae251851e792f0f04377%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-california-iowa-retire-stayed-less-than-2-years-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wendy%20and%20Kurt%20Meyer%20moved%20from%20California%20to%20Iowa%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20family%20in%20retirement.%20But%20they%20quickly%20realized%20they%20didn't%20like%20Iowa%20or%20retirement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22esnodgrass%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Snodgrass)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A363%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-california-iowa-retire-stayed-less-than-2-years-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C