0affordable%20alternative%20to%20renting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHomes%20in%20the%20community%20start%20at%20%24190%2C000%2C%20and%20the%20typical%20monthly%20mortgage%20payment%20is%20around%20%241%2C500.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESouth%20Park%20Cottages%20is%20so%20popular%20that%20its%20developer%20is%20building%20another%20community%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBooker%20Washington%20dreamed%20of%20building%20a%20community%20where%20everyday%20people%20could%20afford%20to%20buy%20a%20home%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20South%20Park%20Cottages%2C%20a%20village%20of%2029%20tiny%20homes%20just%20outside%20Atlanta%20that%20opened%20in%202023%20with%20prices%20from%20%24190%2C000%20to%20%24230%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompare%20that%20to%20the%20typical%20home%20sold%20in%20Atlanta%2C%20which%20Redfin%20found%20cost%20%24431%2C250%20as%20of%20February%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20was%20clear%3A%20All%2029%20homes%20%E2%80%94%20one-%20and%20two-bedroom%20units%20ranging%20from%20400%20to%20650%20square%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20sold%20out%20over%20a%20year%20before%20they%20were%20even%20built%20and%20less%20than%20two%20months%20after%20hitting%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%2C%20the%2041-year-old%20owner%20and%20founder%20of%20micro-home-builder%20Techie%20Homes%2C%20wanted%20to%20offer%20locals%20an%20alternative%20to%20renting%20or%20buying%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etraditional%20single-family%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccessible%20homeownership%20is%20an%20issue%20in%20Atlanta%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20is%20to%20provide%20homes%20at%20a%20price%20point%20where%20mortgages%20are%20equal%20to%20or%20less%20than%20the%20cost%20of%20renting%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20College%20Park%2C%20Georgia%2C%20South%20Park%20Cottages%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20that%20Washington%20is%20building%20a%20second%20community%2C%20Union%20Park%20Cottages%2C%20nearby.%20Sales%20for%20its%2026%20homes%20launch%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Park%20Cottages%20is%20also%20the%20first%20Black-owned%20micro-home%20community%20in%20the%20Atlanta%20area.%20Take%20a%20look%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%202022%2C%20after%20being%20rejected%20by%20investors%20and%20banks%2C%20Washington%20crowdsourced%20%242%20million%20for%20the%20development%E2%80%99s%20construction.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221618%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20first%20sketch%20of%20the%20South%20Park%20Cottages'%20layout.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f4680a3037f8e81750c76b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20sketch%20of%20the%20South%20Park%20Cottages'%20layout.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Techie%20Homes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%20spread%20the%20word%20about%20his%20vision%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20garnering%20support%20from%20locals%20and%20Bianca%20Motley%20Broom%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20College%20Park%20since%202020.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20no%20one%20believed%20in%20my%20dream%2C%20we%20went%20to%20the%20people%20in%20order%20to%20build%20that%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Washington%20said.%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20pent-up%20anger%20in%20urban%20areas%20about%20capital%20equality.%20Even%20if%20it's%20a%20marginal%20investment%20return%2C%20people%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20something%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBackers%2C%20who%20contributed%20amounts%20as%20low%20as%20%241%2C000%2C%20were%20promised%20a%20return%20on%20their%20investment%20once%20the%20homes%20were%20sold%2C%20Washington%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20rate%20of%20return%20was%2012%25%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETechie%20Homes%20acquired%20the%20land%20for%20South%20Park%20Cottages%20for%20%24150%2C000%20in%20October%202021%20and%20construction%20was%20completed%2018%20months%20later.%20%3Cfig