ports%2C%20which%20it%20will%20have%20to%20unload%20onto%20US%20consumers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EChina%20is%20looking%20to%20achieve%20healthier%20growth%20through%20its%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20who%20takes%20over%20the%20White%20House%2C%20an%20overlooked%20boom%20in%20China's%20exporting%20power%20is%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20another%20trade%20clash%20with%20Washington%2C%20Capital%20Economics%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capitaleconomics.com%2Fblog%2Fwhether-its-biden-or-trump-chinas-surplus-fuelling-another-clash-over-trade%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarned%20this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20may%20be%20nervous%20about%20the%20potential%20return%20of%20Mr%20Trump%20and%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20renewed%20trade%20war%2C%20but%20that%20conflict%20looks%20ever%20more%20likely%20whether%20the%20next%20administration%20is%20Democrat%20or%20Republican%2C%26quot%3B%20group%20chief%20economist%20Neil%20Shearing%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.capitaleconomics.com%2Fblog%2Fwhether-its-biden-or-trump-chinas-surplus-fuelling-another-clash-over-trade%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20note%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20face%20value%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20see%20that%20Chinese%20exports%20have%20picked%20up%20in%20any%20meaningful%20way.%20Officially%2C%20China's%20current%20account%20surplus%20remains%20below%20peak%20levels%20in%20its%20share%20of%20global%20GDP.%20But%20Shearing%20notes%20that%20customs%20data%20reveal%20a%20much%20more%20significant%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20points%20out%20that%20the%20surplus-to-GDP%20actually%20stands%20near%20record%20highs.%20He%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20outsized%20lockdown%20demand%20ignited%20China's%20manufacturing%20sector%2C%20and%20output%20has%20jumped%20over%2025%25%20since%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20demand%20has%20now%20slowed%2C%20Chinese%20production%20hasn't.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20China%20Beige%20Book%20CEO%20Leland%20Miller%2C%20that's%20happening%20as%20Beijing%20sees%20manufacturing%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-trade-war-exports-manufacturing-growth-property-crisis-solar-2024-3%5C%22%3Ealternative%20source%20of%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20property%20market.%20Though%20the%20sector%20has%20long%20led%20China's%20prosperity%2C%20it's%20become%20riddled%20with%20debt%20and%20defaults.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20worried%20about%20the%20reckless%20credit%20expansion%2C%20they're%20worried%20about%20the%20property%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20told%20CNBC%20this%20month.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20just%20batten%20down%20the%20hatches%20and%20focus%20on%20national%20security%20priorities%2C%20build%20a%20domestic%20chip%20ecosystem%2C%20you%20know%2C%20solidify%20the%20core%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20concentrate%20on%20advanced%20manufacturing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20both%20Miller%20and%20Shearing%20agree%20that%20this%20strategy%20could%20erupt%20in%20global%20disputes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20unload%20its%20additional%20supply%2C%20Shearing%20says%20China%20will%20have%20to%20look%20beyond%20its%20own%20markets%2C%20as%20domestic%20consumption%20has%20slumped%20excessively%20in%20the%20country.%20That%20puts%20more%20pressure%20on%20foreign%20buyers%2C%20but%20especially%20the%20US%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20given%20that%20China%20now%20makes%20up%2015%25%20of%20global%20manufacturing%20exports%2C%20it%20cannot%20rely%20on%20smaller%20nations%20to%20absorb%20all%20of%20its%20output%2C%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina's%20exporters%20are%20probably%20more%20reliant%20now%20on%20US%20consumers%20than%20they%20were%20when%20the%20trade%20war%20began%20during%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20Shearing%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20deepen%20the%20US's%20trade%20deficit%20with%20China%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%20something%20any%20president%20will%20likely%20want%20to%20avoid.%20Miller%20estimated%20that%20a%20trade%20war%20could%20start%20as%20soon%20as%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Trump%20has%20laid%20out%20plans%20to%20introduce%20seismic-level%20tariffs%2C%20including%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-economic-outlook-recession-inflation-china-tariffs-biden-president-election-2024-3%5C%22%3E60%25%20tax%20on%20Chinese%20goods%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20his%20tenure%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20he%20led%20a%20tit-for-tat%20trade%20war%20with%20Beijing%2C%20with%20many%20of%20its%20policies%20still%20in%20place%20under%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-trade-war-export-manufacturing-property-crisis-biden-trump-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710588841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e84aefce7f1785b2e6b516%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-trade-war-export-manufacturing-property-crisis-biden-trump-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStructural%20changes%20in%20China's%20economy%20mean%20that%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20are%20on%20a%20collision%20course%20over%20trade%20regardless%20of%20who%20wins.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-trade-war-export-manufacturing-property-crisis-biden-trump-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20taught%20at%20TOPGUN%2C%20and%20the%20flying%20and%20dogfighting%20seen%20in%20t