0back%20window%20when%20it's%20closed.%20Instead%2C%20Tesla%20has%20a%20rearview%20camera%20that%20displays%20on%20the%20truck's%20massive%20infotainment%20system.%20But%20Munro%20said%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20gauge%20space%20based%20on%20the%20camera%20alone.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20I'm%20unhappy%20about%20is%20I%20don't%20know%20where%20the%20back%20end%20of%20this%20vehicle%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Munro%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20camera%20says%20I've%20got%20about%20a%20foot%2C%20but%20it%20actually%20is%20more%20like%20an%20inch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20difficulty%20of%20backing%20up%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20Munro%20said%20he%20hit%20a%20%26quot%3Bback%20wall%2C%26quot%3B%20slightly%20bending%20the%20rear%20edges%20of%20the%20truck%20and%20scuffing%20part%20of%20the%20rear%20bumper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20auto%20expert%20is%20far%20from%20the%20first%20to%20express%20frustration%20with%20backing%20up%20in%20the%20Cybertruck.%20Pharrell%20Williams%20appeared%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharrell-williams-parking-tesla-cybertruck-miami-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficulty%20maneuvering%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Cybertruck%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20several%20auto%20experts%20have%20made%20light%20of%20the%20issue%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20see%20a%20darn%20thing%20out%20of%20the%20back%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20cargo%20bed%20cover%20is%20deployed%2C%26quot%3B%20Clint%20Simone%2C%20an%20automotive%20journalist%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Db874e141e50f6571b7ae8c6f247cea49191df3b3731b5067eebd549bfb14f646%26postID%3D65f45a94894bac29c422e28e%26postSlug%3Dtesla-cybertruck-can-be-difficult-to-maneuver-auto-expert-says-2024-3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.edmunds.com%252Fcar-news%252Ftesla-cybertruck-first-drive-review.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEdmunds%3C%