E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20of%20every%20team%20was%20remote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20flexibility%20has%20enabled%20staff%20to%20sustain%20their%20careers%20in%20the%20face%20of%20major%20life%20changes%2C%20several%20employees%20told%20BI.%20It%20has%20also%20helped%20Dell%20to%20be%20placed%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BBest%20Place%20to%20Work%20for%20Disability%20Equality%20Index%26quot%3B%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20February%20Dell%20introduced%20a%20strict%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-hybrid-workers-return-office-three-days-week-progression-innovation-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturn-to-office%20mandate%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20punitive%20measures%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20stay%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20policy%2C%20staff%20were%20told%20that%20from%20May%20almost%20all%20will%20be%20classified%20as%20either%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bremote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-hybrid-workers-remote-employees-are-feeling-deloitte-survey-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHybrid%20workers%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewill%20be%20required%20to%20come%20into%20an%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20office%20at%20least%2039%20days%20a%20quarter%20%E2%80%94%20the%20equivalent%20of%20about%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20internal%20documents%20seen%20by%20BI%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20want%20to%20keep%20working%20from%20home%2C%20staff%20can%20opt%20to%20go%20fully%20remote.%20But%20that%20option%20has%20a%20downside%3A%20fully%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-from-home-remote-work-increased-layoff-risk-job-market-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20not%20be%20considered%20for%20promotion%2C%20or%20be%20able%20to%20change%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20states%3A%20%26quot%3BFor%20remote%20team%20members%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20the%20trade-offs%3A%20Career%20advancement%2C%20including%20applying%20to%20new%20roles%20in%20the%20company%2C%20will%20require%20a%20team%20member%20to%20reclassify%20as%20hybrid%20onsite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20company%20has%20been%20complaining%20about%20this%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20Dell%20staffer%2C%20who%20works%20alongside%20senior%20management.%20The%20employee%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20for%20fear%20of%20reprisals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bin-person%20connections%20paired%20with%20a%20flexible%20approach%20are%20critical%20to%20drive%20innovation%20and%20value%20differentiation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20approach%20differs%20from%20founder%20and%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-of-michael-dell-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichael%20Dell's%3C%2Fa%3E%20previous%20support%20for%20remote%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20told%20CRN%20that%20the%20company's%20expanded%20homeworking%20culture%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20here%20to%20stay.%26quot%3B%20The%20billionaire%20later%20criticized%20companies%20that%20were%20enforcing%20RTO%2C%20writing%20on%20LinkedIn%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20counting%20on%20forced%20hours%20spent%20in%20a%20traditional%20office%20to%20create%20collaboration%20and%20provide%20a%20feeling%20of%20belonging%20within%20your%20organization%2C%20you're%20doing%20it%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20office%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22639%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61768aafe100ad00181d843b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22427%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMichael%20Dell%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Dell.%20%3Cp%3EDell%20Technologies%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20the%20company%20line%20had%20not%20changed%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20long-term%20ambition%20for%20Dell%20Technologies%20is%20for%2060%25%20of%20our%20workforce%20to%20operate%20remotely%20on%20any%20given%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20March%202023%2C%20Dell%20started%20to%20change%20its%20policies%20with%20a%20new%20mandate%20ordering%20all%20staff%20living%20within%20an%20hour%20of%20offices%20to%20come%20in%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20CRN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Cary%20Cooper%2C%20an%20organizational%20psychologist%20and%20cofounder%20of%20the%20National%20Forum%20for%20Health%20and%20Wellbeing%20at%20work%2C%20says%20Dell's%20pivot%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bpanicked%20reaction%20to%20a%20world%20economy%20that's%20not%20very%20buoyant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20occurs%2C%20people%20turn%20inwards.%20They%20think%2C%20maybe%20if%20we%20brought%20everybody%20in%2C%20it'll%20make%20a%20difference.%20We'll%20perform%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSenior%20execs%20somehow%20think%20that%20people%20in%20the%20office%20are%20more%20productive%20than%20at%20home%2C%20even%20though%20there's%20no%20evidence%20to%20back%20that%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20%26quot%3Bpack%20mentality%26quot%3B%20at%20play%2C%20says%20Cooper%2C%20with%20tech%20companies%20trying%20to%20follow%20what%20everybody%20else%20is%20doing%2C%20rather%20than%20continue%20with%20what%20has%20worked%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20on%20the%20chopping%20block%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrustrated%20workers%20at%20Dell%20spoke%20out%20anonymously%20to%20BI%20about%20how%20the%20new%20policy%20will%20affect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20being%20forced%20into%20a%20position%20where%20either%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20staying%20as%20the%20low%20man%20on%20the%20totem%20pole%2C%20first%20on%20the%20chopping%20block%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20workforce%20reduction%2C%20or%20we%20can%20be%20hybrid%20and%20go%20in%20multiple%20days%20a%20week%2C%20which%20really%20affects%20a%20lot%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20staffer%20said%20she%20and%20many%20colleagues%20were%20hired%20on%20remote%20contracts%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dell%20worker%20lives%20about%20a%2045-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20nearest%20office%20and%20works%2010-hour%20shifts%20four%20days%20a%20week.%20However%2C%20traveling%20there%20would%20be%20virtually%20impossible%20given%20she%20no%20longer%20drives%20following%20a%20car%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20many%20of%20her%20colleagues%20would%20find%20it%20very%20challenging%20to%20get%20to%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Approved'%20offices%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Dell%20worker%20is%20already%20feeling%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20new%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell's%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20sites%20includes%2017%20offices%20in%20the%20US%20and%2026%20globally%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20the%20senior%20employee's%20nearest%20office.%20%26quot%3BI%20now%20know%20I%20have%20no%20office.%20So%20I%20am%20remote%2C%20or%20I%20move%20if%20I%20want%20to%20stay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20viewed%20a%20promotion%20offer%20sent%20to%20the%20long-serving%20remote%20worker%20around%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-mandates-creating-huge-disruption-in-workers-lives-experts-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERTO%20mandate%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20accept%20that%20promotion%2C%20the%20employee%20would%20not%20only%20have%20to%20start%20coming%20into%20the%20office%2C%20but%20move%20state%20to%20be%20near%20an%20%26quot%3Bapproved%26quot%3B%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20Round%20Rock%20Texas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d765dbf533b039a885f016%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDell's%20HQ%20in%20Round%20Rock%20Texas%20is%20one%20of%2017%20offices%20approved%20for%20general%20employees.%3Cp%3EBrandon%20Bell%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EGeographically%20divided%20teams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20also%20say%20that%20Dell's%20claims%20about%20fostering%20%26quot%3Bin-person%20connection%26quot%3B%20do%20not%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20common%20for%20teams%20at%20Dell%20to%20be%20spread%20around%20the%20US%20and%20even%20other%20countries%2C%20according%20to%20BI's%20senior%20source%20at%20Dell%2C%20who%20works%20across%20the%20organization%20and%20has%20access%20to%20employee%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20team%20has%20people%20in%20at%20least%20two%20states%2C%20some%20in%20three%20or%20four.%20I%20can't%20think%20of%20one%20team%20where%20everyone%20is%20in%20one%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20person%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20even%20if%20commuting%20distances%20are%20feasible%2C%20many%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20collaborate%20face-to-face%20with%20their%20teams%20in%20the%20same%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Dell%20worker%20told%20BI%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20support%20that%20if%20I%20actually%20had%20team%20members%20that%20were%20local%20and%20would%20actually%20go%20on-site.%20With%20us%20being%20so%20spread%20out%20around%20the%20United%20States%2C%20there's%20really%20no%20point%20in%20us%20going%20in.%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20in%20a%20room%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20who%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20do%20my%20job%20or%20how%20to%20help%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDisproportionate%20impact%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBI's%20senior%20source%20at%20Dell%20used%20their%20access%20to%20pull%20data%20about%20the%20composition%20of%20remote%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20deal%20with%20many%20many%20teams%20across%20our%20business.%20Every%20team%20I%20work%20with%20has%20at%20least%20one%20person%20if%20not%20two%20or%20three%20affected%20by%20this%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20senior%20source%20at%20Dell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20overwhelmingly%20women.%20This%20new%20policy%20on%20its%20face%20appears%20to%20be%20anti-remote%2C%20but%20in%20practice%20will%20be%20anti-woman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%26quot%3BQuiet%20firing%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20also%20said%20they%20believe%20the%20new%20measures%20are%20a%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforcing-workers-back-office-risks-talent-exodus-dell-amazon-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epush%20some%20employees%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20phenomenon%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bquiet%20firing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20level%20of%20micromanagement%20makes%20me%20want%20to%20leave%20Dell%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20since%20the%20announcement%20was%20made%2C%20dozens%20of%20staff%20have%20been%20discussing%20quitting%20in%20Discord%20chats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20staff%20including%20one%20based%20in%20Germany%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20also%20said%20many%20people%20were%20now%20considering%20leaving%20Dell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20last%20year%2C%20Dell%20laid%20off%20about%205%25%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20or%20about%206%2C600%20jobs%2C%20per%20an%20SEC%20filing%2C%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20poor%20PC%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20about%20culture.%20Period%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20senior%20Dell%20worker%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20headcount%20cuts%20that%20need%20to%20happen%20and%20we%20are%20suffering.%20If%20people%20leave%20on%20their%20own%2C%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20out%20severance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECooper%20agreed%20that%20the%20level%20of%20control%20in%20this%20policy%20w