uses%2C%20Moscow%20mansions%2C%20and%20yachts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%229045%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yacht%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f4192f1851e792f0eff6b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMonaco%20Yacht%20show%3Cp%3EMandoga%20Media%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20the%20Russian%20elite%20were%20willing%20to%20throw%20at%20young%2C%20inexperienced%20tutors%20was%20unbelievable%20%E2%80%94%20and%20frankly%20quite%20frightening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20acquaintances%20who%20worked%20as%20governors%20or%20nannies%20who%20were%20earning%20well%20into%20six%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20were%20offered%20similarly%20extortionate%20salaries%20to%20spend%20their%20summers%20teaching%20on%20yachts%20in%20places%20like%20St.%20Barts%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20or%20sailing%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20taught%20in%20luxurious%20villas%20and%20penthouse%20apartments%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOften%20the%20children%20we%20taught%2C%20who%20were%20from%20four%20to%20around%2018%20years%20old%2C%20had%20private%20drivers%20who%20hurried%20them%20about%20in%20tinted%20Range%20Rovers%20or%20Mercedes-Benz%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Moscow%2C%20many%20of%20our%20classes%20took%20place%20in%20Rublevka%2C%20an%20elite%20guarded%20estate%20in%20the%20west%20of%20the%20capital%2C%20where%20Russian%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-kids-names-ages-secret-daughters-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVladimir%20Putin%20owns%20a%20home.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20kids%20we%20taught%20lived%20in%20a%20world%20entirely%20different%20from%20any%20we%20had%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20colleague%20of%20mine%20did%20after-school%20classes%20there%20with%20an%20eight-year-old%20boy%20called%20Ivan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20week%20his%20family%20had%20been%20planning%20a%20weekend%20trip%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20capital%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20the%20weather%20isn't%20too%20bad%20so%20we%20can%20take%20the%20helicopter%20and%20don't%20have%20to%20drive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20homeschooled%20two%20pupils%3A%20Alexei%2C%2013%2C%20and%20his%20younger%20sister%2C%20Elena%2C%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20met%20Alexei%2C%20he%20walked%20into%20our%20office%20sporting%20%241%2C000%20Balenciaga%20trainers%20and%20a%20watch%20worth%20at%20least%20five%20times%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20nevertheless%20a%20pleasant%20child%20but%2C%20like%20Ivan%2C%20appeared%20somewhat%20disconnected%20from%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20class%2C%20he%20was%20shocked%20to%20hear%20that%20we%20didn't%20receive%20regular%20pampering%20from%20staff%20at%20home%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20seven%20months%20since%20you%20had%20a%20massage%3F%20I%20have%20a%20massage%20every%20day%2C%20I%20have%20my%20own%20massage%20therapist%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElena%20was%20less%20communicative%20and%20didn't%20seem%20to%20enjoy%20the%20lavish%20lifestyle%20she%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20have%20I%20done%20to%20deserve%20this%3F%20I%20hate%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20would%20often%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20colleagues%20and%20I%20became%20increasingly%20concerned%20about%20her%20well-being%20as%20time%20went%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20didn't%20enjoy%20classes%20alone%20and%20wanted%20to%20be%20with%20friends%20in%20a%20normal%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20parents%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20seem%20tied%20to%20the%20life%20into%20which%20she%20had%20been%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20job%20constantly%20surprised%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20met%20two%20types%20of%20parents%20in%20the%20job%3A%20Those%20who%20spent%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20on%20their%20children%20because%20they%20cared%20about%20them%2C%20and%20those%2