ts%20went%20through%20skill%20upgradation%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20applicants%20have%20great%20ideas%20but%20are%20not%20savvy%20enough%20to%20write%20a%20proposal%20or%20give%20a%20presentation.%20When%20we%20think%20of%20diversity%2C%20we%20often%20forget%20about%20the%20tribals.%20We%20think%20they%20are%20primitive%20and%20live%20in%20jungles.%20But%20when%20you%20read%20the%20proposals%2C%20you%20learn%20their%20diverse%20wisdom%2C%20culture%20and%20history.%20Through%20this%20fellowship%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20preserve%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Oinam%20Doren%2C%20a%20jury%20member%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20Samvaad%20fellows%202023%20include%20%E2%80%94%20Saka%20Mashangva%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344734%2Ftata-samvaad-jamshedpur-sumanti-devi-artisan-preserves-oraon-art-mud-natural-finger-painting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efolk%20artist%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20wants%20to%20document%20Tingteila%2C%20a%20traditional%20musical%20instrument%20of%20the%20Tangkhul%20tribe%20of%20Manipur%20which%20is%20almost%20extinct%3B%20Santosh%20Pawar%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20who%20wants%20to%20preserve%20and%20promote%20the%20folklore%20of%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%3B%20Madhavi%20Meravi%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20document%20the%20folk%20tales%20of%20Gond%20tribal%20communities%20as%20part%20of%20children%E2%80%99s%20literature%3B%20Pansy%20Jami%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20document%20the%20benefits%20of%20fermented%20food%20from%20the%20Lotha%20Naga%20tribe%20of%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicants%20who%20get%20rejected%20are%20encouraged%20to%20apply%20again%2C%20shared%20Oinam.%20The%20jury%20members%20and%20Samvaad%20team%20continue%20to%20provide%20support%20by%20staying%20in%20touch%20to%20help%20participants%20enhance%20their%20ideas%20or%20pitches%20for%20a%20stronger%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by