the%20day%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20promptly%20fulfil%20her%20duties%20as%20an%20ASHA%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20kidney%20health%3A%20dialysis%2C%20costs%2C%20and%20access%20initiatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealthy%20kidneys%20cleanse%20your%20blood%2C%20removing%20waste%20and%20excess%20fluid%20from%20your%20body%20in%20the%20form%20of%20urine.%20They%20also%20regulate%20acidity%20levels%20and%20contribute%20to%20maintaining%20a%20proper%20balance%20of%20water%2C%20salts%2C%20and%20minerals%20in%20your%20bloodstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20kidneys%20are%20unable%20to%20remove%20enough%20wastes%20and%20fluids%20from%20the%20blood%2C%20it%20causes%20a%20build-up%20of%20toxins%20and%20waste.%20Dialysis%20replaces%20the%20functions%20of%20the%20kidney%20by%20removing%20the%20waste%20and%20excess%20fluid%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Ganpat%20Ram%2C%20Medical%20Officer%20at%20Karnaprayag%20Renal%20Care%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22THF's%20program%20aims%20to%20provide%20quality%20dialysis%20services%20to%20people%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20reducing%20costs%20and%20travel%20time%20to%20improve%20their%20well-being.%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-768x512.jpg