3EAs%20she%20looked%20for%20what%20she%20could%20make%20with%20recycled%20floral%20waste%2C%20she%20came%20across%20a%20small%20business%20near%20her%20house%20who%20used%20cow%20dung%20powder%20to%20make%20incense%20sticks.%20Could%20she%20do%C2%A0the%20same%20with%20flowers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20small%20space%20provided%20by%20her%20brother%2C%20Poonam%20set%20up%20her%20unit.%20From%20June%202019%2C%20she%20will%20get%20up%20at%205%20am%20and%20go%20to%20temples%20near%20her%20residence.%20There%2C%20she%20would%20request%20the%20staff%20to%20give%20her%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20flowers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20obliged%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20mixed%20with%20other%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201242px)%20100vw%2C%201242px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Poonam%20sells%20her%20products%20through%20exhibitions%20and%20her%20website%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913.jpeg%201242w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-300x199.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-500x331.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at-14.19.21-1709639913-768x509.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-04-at